property.description:
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Lodge House Vintage Cabin - Pool Table - Walk to Lake - Summertime Pool&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Originally Potters Camp, a vintage fisherman&amp;#39;s retreat in the early 1900s, our historic lakefront lodge is over a hundred years old yet still caters to mountain visitors looking to enjoy the tranquil waters of Big Bear Lake. Catering to all types of vacationers seeking a unique mountain experience, this rustic yet spacious lakefront property offers the perfect recipe for relaxation and unwinding, from couples and families to large groups for gatherings and special events, this property is perfect for everyone. Managed by Big Bear Vacations, this historic site boasts twelve mountain-style cabins on two acres of pine-shaded lakefront property including direct lake access, a summertime boat dock, playground, and swimming pool.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Lodge House is the original office of this culture-rich property, boasting original wood walls and mountain charm paired with nostalgic vibes and a true rock fireplace where you can enjoy warming your toes together as a family or watching a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV. A full kitchen and dining area sit at the back of the cabin, perfect for preparing home cooked meals and snacks for the day&amp;#39;s adventures. The back patio offers additional dining options and a Charcoal BBQ for you to grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake. The spacious living room pairs perfectly with the open game room to provide plenty of space for memories to be made here in the mountains, the French doors from here lead out to the spacious sun deck complete with patio furnishings and a great view of the summertime pool.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Three spacious bedrooms including the primary suite and private bath are easily accessible within this single level rustic retreat, with private access doors to both guest rooms this is the perfect setup for a group of friends or family vacation to the mountains. Step outside to enjoy this spacious lakefront lodge property, complete with a spacious group dining area, kids&amp;#39; playground, summertime pool, and the spacious lake shore area with boat dock access for guests. Located just a short walk to Big Bear Village and local marinas this truly is an unbeatable location no matter the season you choose to visit!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Full Bed + Twin Bed- Streaming TV, Private Entrance&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: Full/Twin Bunk- Streaming TV, Private Entrance&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3: King Bed, Streaming TV, Private Full Bath&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)&lt;br /&gt;
Private Full Bath- Bedroom 3&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
-Sleeps 8&lt;br /&gt;
-3 Car Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
-2 Pets Welcome w/ Additional Fees&lt;br /&gt;
-1,500 Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
Hotel Permit #:&amp;nbsp;PR0013888&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

