Aspen Grove Log Cabin - Central Big Bear&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for a group of friends or family vacation our Aspen Grove chalet is a fabulous single story log home located within a great central neighborhood, equipped with all that you need for a memorable mountain experience, yet is just a few minutes to hiking, the lake, or even the downtown Village area for shopping or entertainment. Located in a central Fox Farm neighborhood your home is ordained with cozy mountain furnishings, cooking and dining essentials, and a prime central location making this the perfect destination no matter the season you choose to visit Big Bear.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Boasting an open space floor plan you will love having everyone together as you snuggle up on the comfy couches under knotty pine cathedral ceilings and warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace as you watch the snow falling or catch a movie on the TV with complimentary Cable and hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment. The log dining table pairs up with a cute breakfast bar and stools to ensure your group has plenty of space to enjoy your meals together comfortably while the efficient kitchen offers plenty of counter space for meal preparations, general appliances and a dishwasher to ensure that your cleanup is a breeze.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Your single level retreat offers easy and convenient access to your three bedrooms and both bathrooms including the spacious primary suite with it&amp;#39;s own private open bath- all of your rooms are made up for your group with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your visit when you arrive. Venture outside where you will love the tree lined and fenced private back yard area with a cute patio where you can relax and unwind under the stars. Aspen Grove is a fantastic vacation chalet furnished from head to toe with your stay in mind and boasting the essentials and necessities to ensure an unforgettable and relaxing stay can be had any time of the year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
