&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Breezy One- this is the perfect lakeside retreat for a group of friends, family reunion, or couple&amp;#39;s retreat to the mountains boasting all that you need for a memorable and relaxing trip no matter the season you choose to visit. Sitting just a mile from the Big Bear Village and local marinas you have the very best of Big Bear right at your fingertips from this spacious two story chalet. Boasting the necessities from home along with cooking and dining essentials you will have a spacious lakeside yard including a nice patio area, seasonal boat dock, and BBQ area for your enjoyment- the possibilities are endless from here.&lt;br /&gt;
