property.description:
Dreams of Summit - Central Ski Resort Log Cabin Retreat w/ Hot Tub + Games&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Dreams of Summit is the perfect retreat for guests looking to experience the very best of Big Bear! This freshly renovated, log-style chalet is designed with comfort, entertainment, and convenience in mind&amp;mdash;every detail thoughtfully curated to elevate your mountain getaway. Located just below Snow Summit Resort, you&amp;rsquo;ll enjoy unbeatable access to year-round activities including hiking trails, mountain biking, tubing, and the ski and park lifts&amp;mdash;all just a short walk from your doorstep. Whether you&amp;#39;re shooting a game of pool in the loft or strolling through the peaceful neighborhood, endless adventure and relaxation await.&lt;br /&gt;
Step inside the cozy lower-level family room and instantly feel the warmth of a classic mountain lodge. Soaring cathedral ceilings, rich knotty pine accents, and a stunning rock fireplace create the perfect backdrop for unforgettable moments with your group. Settle into the comfy armchairs by the fire or enjoy your favorite movie or game day on the mounted flat-screen TV, complete with cable and high-speed WiFi.&lt;br /&gt;
Beautiful hardwood floors lead you into the formal dining room, featuring a custom log dining table ideal for family meals and group gatherings. Large windows fill the room with natural light and offer serene forest views. From here, access the spacious redwood deck overlooking a private, tree-lined backyard&amp;mdash;an ideal spot for morning coffee or evening relaxation. The fully equipped kitchen will delight the chef of your group, complete with pine cabinetry, ample counter space, essential appliances, a dishwasher, and a charming breakfast bar.&lt;br /&gt;
For added convenience, the chalet includes a dedicated laundry room with a washer and dryer&amp;mdash;perfect for snow gear or extended stays. The entry level offers two guest bedrooms and a full bathroom, along with a convenient half bath off the living area. Each space is prepared with warm linens, cozy blankets, and fresh towels to ensure a comfortable stay.&lt;br /&gt;
Upstairs, you&amp;#39;ll find the spacious master suite featuring a private bathroom with a jetted spa tub, plus an additional sleeping area in the open game room loft. This fun-filled loft also includes a full-size pool table, comfortable lounge seating, and a wet bar&amp;mdash;ideal for entertaining or unwinding with a drink after a day on the mountain.&lt;br /&gt;
Outside, a large redwood deck awaits with outdoor seating and a propane BBQ, perfect for grilling and gathering. The peaceful backyard offers a quiet retreat surrounded by nature&amp;mdash;an ideal place to start your day or wind down in the evening.&lt;br /&gt;
Dreams of Summit lives up to its name, offering a memorable blend of comfort, style, and mountain charm. With its central location just below Snow Summit and only minutes from the lake, marinas, grocery stores, and the Village, you&amp;rsquo;ll be perfectly positioned to enjoy everything Big Bear has to offer.&lt;br /&gt;
Don&amp;rsquo;t miss your chance to experience this exceptional chalet on your next mountain getaway!&lt;br /&gt;
