&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to&amp;nbsp;All About Fun, a beautifully updated log-style chalet in the heart of Big Bear! Perfectly located just minutes from ski resorts, Big Bear Lake, and the downtown Village, this cozy retreat is designed to create unforgettable family vacations or group getaways.&lt;br /&gt;
