property.description:
Moose Creek Chalet w/ Hot Tub&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Your group will love your vacation here at Moose Creek Chalet, our furnished and comfortable two story chalet home boasts a superb Snow Summit Resort location paired with the comforts from home and bonus amenities to add to your experience. Perfect for a family reunion, couples retreat, or a group of friends heading up to enjoy the mountain together this is the perfect chalet to make memories in the alpine together.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You will love the spacious open floor plan here boasting knotty pine-beamed cathedral ceilings and tons of windows letting in the perfect amount of natural lighting while adding views of nature and snow falling outside to your visit. Two separate living and family room areas are perfect for entertaining a large group or dinner party with plenty of space for everyone to enjoy the mountains together. Snuggle up on comfortable couches and enjoy the wood-burning fireplaces in either room or challenge each other at a game of billiards on the pool table. You&amp;#39;ll be able to stay connected while on vacation with modern, streaming (account needed), flat screen TVs.&amp;nbsp; Complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your group to enjoy. In the middle of your two living spaces you will find multiple dining options including a combination of breakfast bar stools and log dining tables to ensure the whole group can make memories together over your meals. The cute kitchen is the hub of the cabin in the middle of the lower level and offers all that the chef of your group will need to whip up your home cooked meals right here at the cabin. This open space is perfect for entertaining a dinner party with ample counter spaces for preparing and tons of updated lighting. The oak cabinets are stocked full with cookware and utensils for your use plus general appliances are available.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You&amp;#39;ll have quick and convenient access to two sleeping quarters and a hallway bathroom on each level of your cabin, all of which are made up for your group with TVs, warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive. A separate laundry area offers a washer and dryer for your wet snow clothes or extended stays right here at the cabin for the ultimate convenience year round. As you venture outside you have a spacious alpine tree lined property all to yourselves with beautiful and relaxing amenities. Enjoy grilling up dinner on the provided propane BBQ and awesome outdoor patio furnishings. The expansive wood sun deck connects to the lower level game room and boasts a relaxing private hot tub under a million stars for your group to enjoy a soak after your fun day of adventure out on the mountain or lake. Moose Creek Chalet offers all that you need to enjoy a relaxing and memorable visit to the mountains no matter the season!&lt;br /&gt;
