property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;A Cozy Red Cabin - Family-Friendly Mountain View Cabin with Wi-Fi, Fireplace, &amp;amp; Deck&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bring the whole family along to this memorable red cabin and enjoy the mountains of Big Bear. You can catch a glimpse of the peaks from your personal deck, which offers plenty of seating for those cool evenings. A fireplace keeps everybody warm and sets the scene for a cozy stay here.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Canoe, kayak, sailing, and paddleboard rentals are available at Pine Knot Marina, just under three miles away. While you&amp;#39;re there, visit Pine Knot Village for great local dining and shopping. Baldwin Stables offers horseback riding for adventurous guests. Winter sports enthusiasts, rejoice: Bear Mountain and Snow Summit are both nearby, and lift tickets and ski rentals can be easily obtained. You&amp;#39;re on the bus route and bike path here, so getting to the slopes or town center is easy.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Kids in particular will love the bunk room, outfitted with four bunk beds. The master bedroom accommodates two on a queen bed. Baby gates and games for all ages are provided for young guests. A provided space heater offers extra warmth if needed.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Preparing meals in this home&amp;#39;s full kitchen is a breeze, and the dishwasher makes cleanup speedy. The cabin&amp;#39;s TVs have Blu-ray and Netflix capability (with your own Netflix login). Free WiFi keeps everybody connected during your stay in the mountains. Please be aware that 4x4 driving may be required during a winter visit.&lt;br /&gt;
Book this bright red mountain getaway for your family&amp;#39;s next Big Bear vacation!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
* The owner of this home has severe allergies, and we request that guests traveling with service animals reserve a different property.&amp;nbsp;Thank you for your understanding, and please contact Big Bear Vacations if you would like assistance finding a different rental.&lt;br /&gt;
