&lt;br /&gt;
Good Times is a super relaxing and fully furnished chalet cabin located within minutes to all that Big Bear has to offer, pairing the necessities from home with added bonus amenities, you will love this spacious flat lot, full of pine trees and a fenced back yard, you will find a seasonal horseshoe pit available in the Summer months. The lower level garages are off limits to guests leaving you with a single story chalet once you climb and arrive at the top of the stairs to the wrapped redwood deck, the perfect place to enjoy the private outdoor spa and BBQ.&lt;br /&gt;
