&lt;br /&gt;
Boulder Creek is a cozy lakeside upper level condo with the essentials needed for your group to experience a great mountain vacation, within a ten minute drive to the resorts or Village and only feet from Boulder Bay Park with lake access for fishing, kayaks and a great grassy area for picnics. Located in a quiet Boulder Creek Resort the complex is a prime year round location sitting right next door to Boulder Bay Park with year round fishing, picnic areas, and kayak rentals. The complex offers a community pool and hot tub for guests use along with a massive flat and open parking area which is the ultimate bonus to this cozy chalet retreat no matter the season you choose to visit Big Bear.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
