property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Popko&amp;rsquo;s Place &amp;ndash; Walk to Snow Summit &amp;amp; Save on Parking | Near Village Dining &amp;amp; the Lake&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Calling all snow lovers, hikers, bikers, and mountain-season adventurers! Popko&amp;rsquo;s Place is your cozy, single-level alpine chalet perfectly positioned for year-round fun. Located just a half-mile walk to the Snow Summit lifts, you can skip parking fees, beat the crowds, and head straight to the slopes or bike park. You&amp;#39;re also just minutes from the Village, the lake, and local dining, making this one of Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s most convenient spots for any getaway.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step inside to a warm, inviting living room designed for relaxation after a day on the mountain. Snuggle up on the plush couches, sip cocoa by the wood-burning fireplace, and stream your favorite shows on the flat-screen TV with complimentary cable and high-speed WiFi. The well-appointed kitchen has everything your chef needs from cookware to general appliances and a dishwasher for easy cleanup. A log dining table and breakfast bar stools offer plenty of cozy seating for shared meals, game nights, or morning coffee by the fire.&lt;br /&gt;
All three bedrooms are conveniently located on one level and come fully prepared with fresh linens, warm blankets, and soft towels so you can settle right in and unwind. Large windows bring in natural light and mountain charm throughout the space.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Outside, enjoy a sunny deck, fenced backyard, and Charcoal BBQ perfect for grilling after a day of adventure. With walking access to Snow Summit (winter skiing, snow tubing, summer bike park, and scenic sky chair rides), endless trails, and Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s top attractions just minutes away, Popko&amp;rsquo;s Place is the ideal base camp for every season.&lt;br /&gt;
Book your stay today and experience your new home away from home in the mountains!&lt;br /&gt;
