&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to I Love View!! Your group will fall in love with our freshly renovated and ultra cozy two story&amp;nbsp;Moonridge&amp;nbsp;home sitting on the perfect hillside property near Bear Mountain Ski Resort and Zoo you will love the forest and lake views in the distance from your expansive redwood deck. Featuring a reverse floor plan paired with the comforts from home and added entertainment our fully furnished chalet is the ultimate vacation home to experience the mountains for a group of friends or small family no matter the season!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Boasting new modern comforts including central forced heat, fresh hardwood floors and paint, and furnished from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind your group will absolutely love this chalet! Being a reverse floor plan you will enter on the lower level where you will find the ultra spacious master suite which offers a relaxing jetted spa tub, sitting chairs, and awesome forested views from the colossal windows. A separate laundry room area here offers a washer and dryer for your convenience to handle your wet snow clothes or extended stays right on site.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Venture upstairs to the main portion of your escape cabin where you will fall in love with this big open family room space, gorgeous hardwood floors pair perfectly with the knotty pine cathedral ceilings and big open windows to offer the perfect amount of natural lighting and comfort. The comfortable and open dining room area at the top of the stairs offers a wonderful space to sit together and enjoy your meals at the formal dining table. Enjoy hanging together in the ultra cozy living room area with new modern furnishings and the comforts from home. An oversized plush couch is sat perfectly in front of the toasty stone wall fireplace and mounted flat screen TV, with Cable and complimentary hi speed WIFI provided by the owners you will love snuggling up here and watching a movie. For added entertainment enjoy a game of shuffleboard together here on the shuffleboard game perfectly situated behind the couch along the wall leading to the kitchen area. The open chef&amp;#39;s kitchen is perfect for entertaining a dinner party and preparing your group or family meals together, an adorable kitchen island turned breakfast bar pairs with ample counter spaces for whipping up meals together. The oak cabinets are freshly stained and stocked with all that you need including cookware, utensils, and new stainless appliances including a dishwasher are available for your added convenience. Two additional bedrooms and an added guest bathroom are easily accessible here on the upstairs level, all are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels upon arrival.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Outside your home you will find an amazing alpine environment, your tree lined property sits hillside with amazing forest and distant lake views from the wrapped redwood sun deck. Ample outdoor patio furnishings pair with a propane BBQ to provide you a great space to relax and grill up dinner in the evenings or sip your first cup of coffee among the birds and pine trees in the mornings. The spacious tree lined property is private yet very central keeping your group within ten minutes to all local activities like the lake or Village shops and especially close to Bear Mountain Resort for skiing, hiking, golf or the newly reopened Alpine Zoo!&lt;br /&gt;
