&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Circle Views!! Your group will absolutely love our spacious and freshly renovated two story retreat, furnished with all that you need for a memorable and relaxing visit, and located in a quiet lakeside neighborhood of Boulder Bay just a block to lake access, fishing, and picnic areas at Boulder Bay Park. Our owners have taken your vacation stay into mind when renovating this lovely chalet, complete with entertaining game tables, gourmet kitchen essentials, modern amenities, and a great central location.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Climb the stairs from the driveway up to the massive enclosed sun deck where you can enjoy outdoor patio furnishings and the most amazing valley and sunset views, this is the perfect spot to sip your first cup of coffee in the mornings or watch the sun setting over the lake in the evenings. Enter your cozy family room to be greeted with knotty pine wood accents, hardwood floors, and big open windows- you will immediately feel like you have your very own mountain lodge to yourselves for your trip.&amp;nbsp; Leather sitting arrangements around the toasty wood burning fireplace offers a great space to snuggle up together and warm your toes as you enjoy a movie on the mounted flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment. Air-hockey and foosball tables keep the group entertained in this spacious open floor plan which leads right into the gourmet kitchen and equipped dining area which are complete with onyx counter tops, oak cabinets, stainless appliances, and exactly what you need to whip up home cooked slope side snacks or host your next family holiday feasts right here at the cabin. Head out from the dining room area to the fenced back yard and covered patio which is where you are sure to spend most of your time here in the mountains- grilling up your freshly caught dinner from the lake on the propane BBQ and relaxing under the stars.&lt;br /&gt;
