&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for those looking to experience a true log cabin in the woods our Eagle Ridge Views home has all that you need for a comfortable and relaxing alpine vacation! Our spacious two story chalet is furnished from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind, packed with modern amenities paired with the essential necessities from home to ensure your group has a wonderful experience. Located in the prestigious &amp;quot;Castle Glen Estates&amp;quot; neighborhood of Big Bear you will be in a prime location close to all local activities year round including both ski resorts, grocery stores, the lake, and even the downtown Village area for dining and shopping- hop in the car and you are under ten minutes to anything your group desires.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Entering into the grand family room on the lower level you are greeted with custom slate floors and updated mountain furnishings and d&amp;eacute;cor, paired perfectly with the vaulted knotty pine cathedral ceilings and soaring windows you will find the perfect balance of natural lighting and gorgeous views to enjoy your time together. Leather sitting couches are sat perfectly in front of the soaring rock fireplace and mounted flat screen Streaming TV and complimentary hi speed WIFI provided for your use this is a great spot to snuggle up in front of the fire and enjoy a movie while watching the snow falling outside. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) You will love the open floor plan, perfect for entertaining a dinner party or a group meal together with the dining room and kitchen area connected to the family room on this lower level. The custom dining table provides the perfect space to enjoy your meals together as a group while the big open windows provide awesome views and direct deck access. The chef of your group will absolutely love the equipped kitchen boasting gorgeous counter space and oak cabinets stocked with cookware and utensils while stainless appliances including a dishwasher ensure your meals here are a breeze!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This lower entry level is home to a guest half bath and separate laundry room with a washer and dryer available for those wet snow clothes or long term stays along with the modern Master Suite which offers the most amazing jetted spa tub and steam shower in the private bathroom. Venturing upstairs you will find an open loft bedroom with two additional bedrooms accessed through the loft and a shared full guest bath to keep things convenient. All of your bedrooms and bathrooms are completely made up for your stay with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels. As an added bonus to this already spectacular vacation home, the garage has been fully converted into a cozy and packed game room which boasts a mini air-hockey table, pool table and sit-down arcade game for your entertainment. Outside you will find expansive wrapped redwood sun decks with outdoor patio furnishings, this is the perfect spot to relax and unwind in the evenings and enjoy grilling up dinner or sipping your first cup of coffee in the mornings among the birds.&lt;br /&gt;
