Retreat to Fox Farm Central Log Cabin| Foosball | Firepit&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Escape to Retreat to Fox Farm, a cozy log cabin perfect for families, couples, or friends seeking a peaceful mountain getaway. Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in a serene, tree-lined neighborhood, this single-level cabin offers the best of Big Bear with easy access to the lake, ski resorts, hiking trails, and the Village&amp;mdash;all within 10 minutes by car.&lt;br /&gt;
Step into the warm, inviting family room with knotty pine cathedral ceilings, a colossal wood-burning rock fireplace, and mountain-themed d&amp;eacute;cor. Relax on comfy sofas, enjoy the flat-screen TV with cable and high-speed Wi-Fi, or challenge your group to a game of foosball while taking in mountain views.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The open floor plan connects the living area to a fully equipped kitchen, complete with modern appliances, ample counter space, and a dishwasher for easy cleanup. A custom log dining table and breakfast bar provide plenty of seating for meals and gatherings.Three spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms ensure comfort for everyone, with fresh linens, blankets, and towels provided. A separate laundry area with a washer and dryer adds convenience for longer stays or snowy adventures.&lt;br /&gt;
Step outside to your private, fully fenced backyard featuring a spacious sun deck, patio seating, and a propane firepit. Whether enjoying morning coffee, stargazing, or watching the kids play in the snow, this space is perfect for unwinding.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Located just two miles from Bear Mountain Resort and close to grocery stores, the marina, and the Alpine Zoo, this cabin offers year-round activities for all ages. With its charming d&amp;eacute;cor, modern amenities, and prime location, Retreat to Fox Farm is the ideal home base for your next Big Bear adventure. Book now and make unforgettable memories!&lt;br /&gt;
