&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Cottage In the Pines | Romantic Couple&amp;#39;s Retreat | Walk to Ski Shuttle&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to our cozy, pet-friendly couple&amp;rsquo;s retreat in the woods at Big Bear! Enjoy an easy walk to the ski shuttle for Bear Mountain Ski Resort, with Bear Mountain Golf Course and the Big Bear Alpine Zoo just down the street. Cottage In the Pines is the perfect destination for couples looking to enjoy a relaxing and romantic mountain getaway complete with everything you need for a memorable stay, no matter the season. This adorable chalet sits just below Bear Mountain and offers a spectacular year-round location with local activities right at your fingertips. Hop in the car and you&amp;rsquo;re within a short ten-minute drive to the ski resorts, grocery stores, marinas, and even the downtown Village for shopping and entertainment.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter to find a cute and cozy open floor plan main room with a comfy couch&amp;mdash;perfect for snuggling up together and warming your toes in front of the toasty wood-burning fireplace. Pop on a movie on the mounted flat screen Smart TV and enjoy complimentary high-speed Wi-Fi provided by the owners. Beautiful hardwood floors pair with knotty pine wall accents and big open windows, offering the perfect balance of natural light and peaceful forest views (and snow falling outside in winter!). The equipped kitchen includes everything you need to whip up home-cooked meals, including cookware, utensils, general appliances, and two mini fridges.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The bistro-style dining table and breakfast bar stools offer plenty of options for meals together. The bedroom and bathroom are cozy and comfortable, and each is prepared for your arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels. Out back, the sunny deck offers patio furnishings and a propane BBQ&amp;mdash;perfect for grilling up your freshly caught lake dinner as you unwind beneath the pine trees. Start your mornings with a stroll down to the newly remodeled Moonridge Corridor to catch the ski shuttle or grab doughnuts and coffee nearby. And since we&amp;rsquo;re pet-friendly, your furry companion can join you for the fun too. Cottage in the Pines has exactly what you need for a romantic, relaxing mountain escape&amp;mdash;your possibilities are endless from this home away from home!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom: Queen Bed&lt;br /&gt;
