&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to our rustic basecamp family retreat at Big Bear. Perfect for a getaway with friends or family vacation this vintage mountain cabin sits right at the base of Snow Summit Resort with direct resort lift access within a quick walk from your door. Hop in the car and you are within ten minutes to local activities including the grocery stores, marina, and downtown Village shops.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
