property.description:
Above It All Big Bear &amp;ndash; Breathtaking Views, Adventure at Your Doorstep&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Escape to Above It All Big Bear, a beautifully updated mountain cabin where stunning views and unbeatable location come together for the perfect getaway. Nestled in a peaceful Bear City neighborhood on Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s scenic north side, this cozy retreat places you just minutes from Holcomb Valley&amp;rsquo;s legendary OHV trails, the iconic Holcomb Pinnacles climbing area, and countless hiking adventures&amp;mdash;all while still being within a quick 10-minute drive to the slopes, grocery stores, and The Village.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Wake up to crisp mountain air and panoramic views of the surrounding peaks. Enjoy your morning coffee or fire up the propane BBQ on the spacious front deck, outfitted with comfortable patio seating. Whether you&amp;#39;re looking to relax or explore, this home offers the best of both worlds. Inside, you&amp;#39;ll find a warm, open concept living space with modern mountain charm. Kick back on plush couches around the wood-burning fireplace and stream your favorite shows on the mounted flat-screen TV with complimentary high-speed Wi-Fi. The fully equipped kitchen has everything you need&amp;mdash;from cookware to a dishwasher&amp;mdash;to make home-cooked meals a breeze, with a dining area that opens right onto the deck for effortless indoor-outdoor living.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This single-level chalet (after a short stair climb to the front door) features two welcoming bedrooms and a full bath, all thoughtfully prepared with fresh linens, blankets, and towels to ensure a comfortable stay. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re here for hiking, climbing, off-roading, or simply soaking in the peaceful views, Above It All is the ideal launchpad for four-season fun in Big Bear. With Oktoberfest, forest trails, and outdoor recreation all close by, your next mountain adventure is just around the corner.&lt;br /&gt;
