property.description:
Mountain Modern Big Bear | Walk to Village-Hot Tub&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
No matter the season, this fresh and bright single level &amp;quot;Mountain Modern&amp;quot; retreat is sure to please your entire group! Recently renovated with ultra fresh furnishings, a full kitchen with cooking essentials, and bonus modern amenities to ensure an unforgettable experience can be had here. Located in the downtown area of Big Bear you will be within a short stroll to local hiking trails, Snow Summit Resort, or even the Village shops and the lake. You will love this ultra central location, perfect for any season!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You will enter into a warm and cozy open concept living room, where you are immediately greeted with custom hardwood floors, freshly painted walls, and adorable modern furnishings, the attention to details here are endless. You will love the perfectly positioned leather sitting couches where you can cuddle up and warm your toes together in front of the toasty gas faux log fireplace and pop on a movie on the mounted flat screen TV with complimentary Cable and hi speed WIFI internet supplied for your enjoyment.&amp;nbsp;The open and bright dining area offers table seating for meals at the crisp and bright dining table with seating for your meals while the equipped and modern kitchen boasts all that you need for whipping up your home cooked meals during your stay. Cookware and stainless steel appliances pair perfectly with the open concept and wonderful breakfast island plus a dishwasher is available for your convenience. Being a single level chalet you will have quick and direct access to a separate laundry room area that has a washer and dryer for those long term stays or wet snow clothes. A shared hallway guest bath along with two guest rooms are paired perfectly with the spacious Master Suite and private master bathroom, all are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your group.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Venturing outside to the great outdoors you will find a private fenced front yard along with a gorgeous back deck area that is sprawling in alpine space and privacy for your group. You will love sitting out on the new patio furnishings while grilling up dinner on the provided natural gas BBQ. Take a soak in your own private hot tub under the pine trees while looking for shooting stars, this is the perfect space to unwind after a wonderful day of adventures out on the mountain. Pairing fine amenities and the comforts from home this is the perfect destination for any group to visit the mountains. No matter your occasion or the season you choose to visit , get yourselves up to Big Bear so that you too can enjoy an exceptional experience here at our Mountain Modern retreat chalet.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
