property.description:
Knotty and Nice Relaxing Retreat Cabin w/ Hot Tub&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Knotty and Nice is a fantastic two-story log home that is furnished from head to toe with the ultimate vacation stay in mind, boasting comfortable furnishings and the necessities from home paired with added fun and a prime central location, you will absolutely love it here!! You will love the easy level driveway parking year round sitting atop a nicely manicured and landscaped mountain property covered in tall pines. Take a short stroll to the lake at Holloways Marina for a boat rental or Pirate Ship Tour or hop in the car and you are minutes to the Village or ski resorts in the winter months.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Your entry level living room is nicely furnished with natural wood features and knotty pine beamed ceilings giving you the true feeling of your own log cabin in the woods for your vacation. Comfortable couches and a lounge chair are sat perfectly in front of the toasty wood burning corner fireplace for you to enjoy snuggling up and watching the snow fall through the big open windows. Host a fun movie night in at the cabin on the flat screen TV tucked conveniently under the stairs, the owners provide Cable and complimentary hi speed WIFI for your enjoyment. The open space floor plan is great for entertaining and leads right to the dining area and your equipped kitchen where the chef of your group will find all that you will need to whip up your home cooked meals right here at the cabin. Custom log furnishings including a gorgeous dining table and barstools are available to ensure there is plenty of space for the whole group to make memories together over meals. The oak cabinets are stocked full with cookware and utensils for your use while stainless appliances including a dishwasher ensures that your cleanup here at Knotty and Nice is a breeze!!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy quick and convenience access to a guest bedroom and bathroom on this entry level along with a separate laundry room area offering a washer and dryer for your added convenience for those wet snow clothes or extended vacation stays. Upstairs you will find two more spacious bedrooms and an added hallway bathroom, all of which are made up for your group with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive for your vacation. Stepping outside you will love this alpine atmosphere surrounded by pine trees and nature boasting two spacious sun decks including plenty of outdoor patio furnishings and a Charcoal BBQ for your group to enjoy grilling up your freshly caught dinner from the lake. Enjoy soaking up your day of adventure in your own private in-deck hot tub under a million stars after a fun day of adventures out on the lake or mountain. Knotty &amp;amp; Nice has it all, pairing a wonderful central location with comfortable and inviting amenities to ensure guests can make the most of their vacation with lifelong memories here at Big Bear!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1:&amp;nbsp;Full/Twin Bunk- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: King Bed, TV w/ Cable- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3: Queen Bed, TV w/ Cable, Game Table- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
