&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for a small family or group of friends looking to experience a relaxing and scenic retreat to the mountains our adorable Moonridge home lives up to it&amp;#39;s name as your group will be able to enjoy Scenic views from every angle of this wonderful single story retreat. Located in a central neighborhood location you&amp;#39;ll be minutes to all local activities with nature truly right outside your back door. Live comfortably with the essentials from home and the most amazing ski slope views from your private sun deck, you can&amp;#39;t beat this great location no matter the season!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Your group will love this ultra cozy cabin boasting an open space floor plan that is perfect for entertaining and making memories together under the pines. Upon entry you will find your equipped kitchen and family room areas, providing the perfect space to enjoy your time together. Vaulted cathedral pine beamed ceilings and a stone floor to ceiling fireplace will make you will feel as if you have your own mountain lodge to yourselves for your trip while the colossal floor to ceilings windows provide ample natural lighting and great viewing points for watching the snow fall or peeking at the ski slopes in the winter months. Enjoy snuggling up on the couch and enjoying a movie night in on the massive flat screen TV or snuggle up in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace, with Cable and complimentary hi speed WIFI provided for your enjoyment. The adorable yet efficiently equipped kitchen has all that the chef of your group will need to whip up your home cooked meals or entertain a small dinner party. The custom log dining bar offers spacious bar stool seating for four and doubles as extra counter prep space. The oak cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils for your group while general appliances and a dishwasher ensures that your cleanup here is a breeze!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You will love the quick and easy access to both bedrooms and your hallway bathroom here within this spacious single level retreat, all of your beds are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your party upon arrival. A separate washer and dryer are conveniently located in one of the rooms to provide convenience for those wet snow clothes or long term visits as well. Venturing out to the massive redwood sun deck you are greeted with endless scenic mountain and ski slope views, you will love relaxing here while sipping your first cup of coffee in the mornings among the birds.&amp;nbsp; A propane BBQ pairs with ample outdoor patio furnishings and a picnic table for you to relax in the evenings and take in this natural alpine environment. Scenic Retreat is furnished with all that you need for a great mountain vacation, with a wonderful view, fabulous location, and cozy at-home feel, what&amp;#39;s a better place to spend your stay while here in Big Bear?!&lt;br /&gt;
