&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Fisherman&amp;#39;s Paradise! Perfect for a group of friends or family vacation this spacious and fully furnished mountain lake house is the ultimate space to spend your next vacation to the mountains, boasting all that your group needs for a perfect trip, situated on the west end of the lake in deep water with a dock, making this cabin a true &amp;quot;Fisherman&amp;#39;s Paradise&amp;quot;. Hop in the car and your party is within a quick ten minute car ride to the ski resorts or Village or take a short stroll over to Holloways marina about a block away for summertime boat rentals and the local Pirate Ship tour- the possibilities are endless from this spacious family lake house.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter on the upper level into the cozy living room area you are greeted with spacious vaulted knotty pine ceilings and big open lake-view windows that let in the perfect balance of natural lighting and beautiful views of the snow falling over the lake right outside. You will love snuggling on the comfy couches as you warm your toes together in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace and pop on a movie on the flat screen TV with Cable and complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment. The chef of your group will love the modern and equipped kitchen boasting all that you need for whipping up home cooked meals and holiday feasts including stainless steel appliances and a dishwasher to ensure your cleanup is a breeze plus ample dining options are available between the custom dining table and breakfast bar stools so your group can enjoy your meals together comfortably.&lt;br /&gt;
