property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Fawnskin Chalet | Dual-Unit Retreat | Hot Tub, Game Room, Dog Run | Walk to Lake &amp;amp; Marina&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Fawnskin Chalet, a newly upgraded and exceptionally spacious open-concept duplex retreat designed for large families, groups, and multi-family stays in Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s peaceful North Shore Fawnskin community. This rare dual-unit layout offers privacy and togetherness in one seamless mountain escape, surrounded by towering pines and breathtaking treetop views overlooking the Big Bear Eagle habitat of Jackie and Shadow. Set less than a mile from the lake and within walking distance to Fawnskin Marina and historic downtown Fawnskin, this chalet delivers unmatched access to nature, water activities, hiking trails, and OHV routes&amp;mdash;while remaining quiet, scenic, and secluded.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The duplex design features two separate entrances, double kitchens, double dining areas, and multiple living spaces connected by a central family room, creating a perfect balance of shared gathering and private retreat. With no shared interior walls between sleeping areas, this layout is ideal for extended families, friends, or group travel. Enjoy hardwood floors, large windows, and open sightlines throughout. Each wing includes a full kitchen with oak cabinetry, dishwashers, and full bathrooms for added convenience. Multiple living rooms feature flat-screen TVs, decorative fireplaces, and direct access to patio decks with majestic forest and treetop views.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping spaces include loft-style landing areas with bunk beds and spacious bedrooms connected by Jack-and-Jill bathrooms, maximizing comfort and functionality for groups of all ages. The garage-converted game room adds a fun, social element with a pool table, dartboard, beer pong table, and streaming TV&amp;mdash;perfect for evenings in after a day of adventure. Step outside to a fully fenced backyard designed for relaxation and play. This home is very pet friendly, featuring a dedicated dog run, multiple outdoor access points, patio seating, propane BBQ, and a private spa tucked among the trees. It&amp;rsquo;s an ideal space to unwind, entertain, and enjoy the mountain air. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re planning a family holiday, group getaway, or outdoor-focused retreat, Fawnskin Chalet delivers space, flexibility, and location in one of Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s most scenic settings.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Please note: Access is via an unmaintained dirt road. In winter, 4x4 and/or chains are required.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
