property.description:
Alpine Chalet Family Getaway ~ Walk to Village&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Alpine Chalet, your year-round mountain retreat perfectly suited for families, groups, and even your four-legged friends. Nestled in a quiet, tree-lined neighborhood in the heart of Big Bear, this beautiful single-story cabin offers modern comfort with the charm of a classic alpine escape. Walk to the historic Big Bear Village for dining and shopping or step onto the nearby Town Trail for a scenic hike, mountain bike ride, or ski directly to Snow Summit for easy resort access. Freshly renovated with your comfort in mind, Alpine Chalet features vaulted knotty pine ceilings, hardwood floors, and mountain-inspired decor. The open living area offers plenty of natural light, a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The fully stocked kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, a dishwasher, and all the cookware needed for home-cooked meals, plus a large log dining table and breakfast bar for gathering together.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The home offers three bedrooms and two updated bathrooms, all made up with fresh linens and towels upon your arrival. Two bedrooms open to a spacious redwood deck with comfortable seating, perfect for sipping morning coffee or unwinding after a day of mountain adventure. A private laundry room adds convenience for longer stays or wet winter gear.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Only four minutes from Pine Knot Marina for lake access, Alpine Chalet places you in the center of Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s best offerings while giving you the peace and privacy of your own log cabin in the woods. Whether you&amp;#39;re here for summer hiking, winter skiing, or a relaxing weekend with loved ones, this pet-friendly getaway is ready to welcome you.&lt;br /&gt;
