property.description:
Black Diamond Chalet~ Luxury Ski-In Bear Mountain&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Black Diamond Chalet, an extraordinary and spacious ski-in/ski-out retreat that offers unparalleled access to the best of Big Bear. Situated directly across the street from Bear Mountain Ski Resort, this luxurious home provides unbeatable slope-side convenience during the winter, while year-round activities such as hiking trails, Big Bear Zoo, and the renovated Rathbun Creek Trail are just steps away.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Recently updated, the chalet boasts all-new bedding, fresh interior paint featuring stunning (T&amp;amp;G) wood paneling, and bold black beam accents, creating an inviting and modern mountain aesthetic. As you step inside, you&amp;rsquo;ll be greeted by high vaulted knotty pine ceilings, bright open windows showcasing breathtaking views, and d&amp;eacute;cor that evokes the ambiance of your own private ski lodge. Relax in style with comfortable furnishings, complimentary high-speed internet, wood burning and faux log gas fireplaces, and new flat-screen streaming TVs (guests must use their own accounts for streaming). The chef in your group will love the spacious and well-equipped kitchen, complete with double ovens, a dishwasher, general appliances, cookware, and plenty of dining space&amp;mdash;perfect for family meals or celebrations.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping arrangements are plentiful, with 4 bedrooms in the main house, a separate game room with additional sleeping accommodations, and a detached bunkhouse featuring 12 queen bunks. With so much space, everyone in your group will have room to relax and unwind. Step outside to enjoy the expansive redwood wraparound decking with patio furnishings and a gas BBQ for grilling. The detached game room provides endless entertainment, offering ping-pong, billiards, and foosball, while the enclosed outdoor hot tub invites you to soak away the day&amp;rsquo;s adventures in total comfort.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Black Diamond Chalet truly has it all, combining a prime year-round location with luxurious amenities to create an unforgettable vacation experience. Whether you&amp;#39;re hitting the slopes or enjoying the serene mountain surroundings, this ultra-unique Big Bear home promises memories that will last a lifetime!&lt;br /&gt;
