Recently updated, the chalet boasts all-new bedding, fresh interior paint featuring stunning (T&amp;amp;G) wood paneling, and bold black beam accents, creating an inviting and modern mountain aesthetic. As you step inside, you&amp;rsquo;ll be greeted by high vaulted knotty pine ceilings, bright open windows showcasing breathtaking views, and d&amp;eacute;cor that evokes the ambiance of your own private ski lodge. Relax in style with comfortable furnishings, complimentary high-speed internet, wood burning and faux log gas fireplaces, and new flat-screen streaming TVs (guests must use their own accounts for streaming). The chef in your group will love the spacious and well-equipped kitchen, complete with double ovens, a dishwasher, general appliances, cookware, and plenty of dining space&amp;mdash;perfect for family meals or celebrations.&lt;br /&gt;
