&lt;br /&gt;
Black Diamond Chalet truly has it all, combining a prime year-round location with luxurious amenities to create an unforgettable vacation experience. Whether you&amp;#39;re hitting the slopes or enjoying the serene mountain surroundings, this ultra-unique Big Bear home promises memories that will last a lifetime!&lt;br /&gt;
