property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Pleasant Pause Family Retreat | Across from Lake | Fawnskin, Big Bear&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Pleasant Pause Family Retreat, a newly upgraded and cozy single-story mountain cabin perfectly positioned on the North Shore of Big Bear Lake in Fawnskin. Surrounded by towering pines with majestic treetop views and direct sightlines to the Big Bear Eagle habitat of Jackie and Shadow, this inviting home delivers comfort, space, and an unbeatable walkable location.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Just steps from the lake and Captain John&amp;rsquo;s Marina, and a short stroll to historic downtown Fawnskin, this retreat makes it easy to enjoy lake days, marina activities, and peaceful mountain charm while staying under ten minutes from Big Bear Village, ski resorts, dining, and shopping.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Inside, the home is warm, spacious, and family friendly, featuring a cozy mountain-style living room with plush seating, a wood-burning fireplace, flat-screen TV with cable, and high-speed Wi-Fi. The newly renovated kitchen is fully equipped with oak cabinetry, modern appliances, dishwasher, and everything needed for home-cooked meals and apr&amp;egrave;s-adventure snacks. A charming dining area brings everyone together to share meals and memories. This single-level layout offers easy access to three comfortable bedrooms and beautifully appointed bathrooms, all prepared with fresh linens, towels, and cozy bedding. A dedicated laundry room with washer and dryer adds convenience for longer stays and winter gear.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step outside to enjoy peaceful patio and sun deck spaces, perfect for morning coffee among the birds or evening relaxation under the trees. Fire up the charcoal BBQ and unwind in the crisp mountain air after a day on the lake or slopes.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
