Kit Kat&amp;#39;s Hideaway- Central Retreat w/ Hot Tub &amp;amp; Games&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Kit Kat&amp;#39;s Hideaway. Our spacious chalet offers the best of Big Bear right at your fingertips paired with the comforts from home and is the perfect setting for a group getaway, family vacation, or couple&amp;#39;s trip to the mountains any time of the year. Located within a short stroll to the lake, local parks, or even the Village this getaway chalet offers a prime central location just minutes from activities and adventure.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Being a single level retreat the open floor plan is perfect for entertaining and staying connected to your group boasting a warm and inviting living room, equipped chef&amp;#39;s kitchen and dining area, plus a game room garage packed with hours of entertainment right here at the cabin. Snuggle up on the cozy couch together and warm your toes in front of the toasty fireplace or pop on a movie on the flat screen TV with Cable available. The game room garage is where you&amp;#39;ll spend most of your time playing games on the pool table, foosball table, or arcade game- this chalet truly has it all!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Venture outside to the great outdoors where you have a relaxing forested oasis all to yourself within the private fully fenced backyard. Relax on the hammock and ready your favorite book or soak up the sun on the cute sun deck, complete with patio furnishings and a propane BBQ grill. Unwind and soak those muscles as you search for shooting stars in your own private hot tub under the pines- you will love spending your evenings here after a fun day out on the mountain. Come experience your new home away from home here at Kit Kat&amp;#39;s Hideaway today!&lt;br /&gt;
