property.description:
Palms To Pines Relaxing Sugarloaf Log Cabin Chalet&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for a group of friends or family vacation our Palms to Pines chalet is a sweet two-story log cabin retreat furnished and decorated from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind. Your group is sure to enjoy an amazing vacation experience here together under the pines on a level and spacious tree lined Sugarloaf lot where you can enjoy peace and relaxation with nature yet still be connected as you will be located within a ten-minute drive to all that Big Bear has to offer. Your group will have all that you need to make memories and enjoy the mountains no matter the season here!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter on the lower level where you are greeted with beautiful knotty pine beamed ceilings and big open windows to take in the forest views and snow falling during the winter months. You will love the cozy and relaxing living room area that is perfect for snuggling up and watching a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV with Amazon Fire Stick and complimentary hi speed WIFI provided for your enjoyment. The toasty wood burning rock fireplace in the corner is a beautiful accent to the cabin and keeps your group comfortable year round.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Around the corner here on your entry level is the adorable kitchen, equipped with the essentials needed for your chef to whip up your home cooked meals right here at the cabin. Oak cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils while general appliances and counter space ensures your meal preparations and cleanup are a breeze. Through the kitchen area you will find your first bedroom and bathroom along with a convenient washer and dryer for those wet snow clothes or extended vacation stays here in the mountains.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Upstairs you will find an additional bathroom and the other two bedrooms, each offers amazing natural lighting from the cute window along with knotty pine ceiling and wall accents and ultra comfortable beds which are made up for your arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your party when you arrive for your vacation.&amp;nbsp;Venturing outside you will love this spacious alpine property, the cute sun deck is a great space to soak up the sunshine here at 7,000 feet or enjoy the private yard full of pine trees and the front patio for sipping your first cup of coffee in the mornings. Palms to Pines is an ultra-relaxing and most serene alpine retreat featuring all that you need to make the most of your next Big Bear stay!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
