property.description:
Grand Forest Lodge Group Retreat&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;Hot Tub &amp;amp; Games&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Grand Forest Lodge is your next home away from home here in the mountains, our beautiful log style lodge is sprawling in square footage and ordained with all that you need for a memorable vacation to Big Bear no matter the season! Located in the Moonridge area of Big Bear you are secluded yet centrally located within literally minutes to all local activities yet are especially close to the Bear Mountain Resort for skiing, hiking, and golf. Enjoy sole access to your main house plus casita suite along with a packed game room, gourmet kitchen and dining facilities, and a private hot tub under the stars, all rooms and spaces are furnished and ready for your arrival with the ultimate vacation experience in mind no matter the season you choose to visit Big Bear.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
