Woodland Log Cabin | Hot Tub, Trailhead &amp;amp; Games&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Woodland Log- your group will fall in love with this fully furnished and custom built two story log cabin chalet, tucked in the trees just outside of the Big Bear Village area our owners have furnished and renovated their home with your vacation experience in mind providing you with all that you need to relax and unwind here in the alpine. Boasting fine amenities and custom d&amp;eacute;cor throughout you will have the best of Big Bear at your fingertips here as you enjoy your time together in the mountains under the pine trees. Take a short stroll to the Village shops for dining or the marina for boat rentals, fishing and tours and you are just a quick three blocks over to Snow Summit Resort for summertime bike park and wintertime ski park access to the lifts. You can&amp;#39;t beat this location year round!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter your chalet where you are immediately greeted with oak wood accent walls, knotty pine beamed ceilings, and massive amounts of windows that let in the perfect balance of natural lighting and wonderful forested mountain views. The cozy living room offers leather couches sat in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace where you can warm your toes and pop on a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV with Cable and complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided by the owners for your enjoyment. Multiple dining areas are set up with comfortable furnishings to ensure your group can enjoy your home cooked meals and holiday feasts here together at the cabin. The chef of your group will absolutely love the gourmet kitchen here at Woodland Log- gorgeous oak cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils along with ample counter space and stainless appliances. Enjoy direct access from here out to the spacious private yard, beautiful sun deck, Charcoal BBQ, and your private hot tub under the pines where you will love soaking up your day of adventures under the stars.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This entry level hosts easy and convenient access to a spacious laundry area and storage room that is perfect for your snow gear and lake toys with a washer and dryer being a must if traveling with kids for those wet snow clothes or extended visits to the mountains. The primary suite is so spacious with double beds and offers its own private 3/4 bath and deck access out to the private hard and hot tub area plus a spacious hallway guest bath is also available for your group. Upstairs you will find two additional sleeping quarters, one with balcony access, and another beautiful bathroom for the group, each room boasts amazing cathedral ceilings, warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive for your vacation. You will love dining out back on the beautiful sun deck or relaxing in the hot tub on the patio. This hillside location is a fabulous ski hill in the winter months providing endless hours of sledding on site when there is snow on the ground! Come experience Woodland Log today!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
