property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Luxury Lodge Estate | Walk to Big Bear Village | Hot Tub &amp;amp; Game Room | Pet Friendly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Luxury Lodge Estate, a grand yet cozy multi-level mountain retreat designed for the ultimate Big Bear getaway. Perfectly positioned just a short walk from Big Bear Village, the lake, shopping, and dining, this upscale short-term rental blends modern luxury with classic alpine charm, making it ideal for family vacations, group trips, and special celebrations year-round.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This ultra-spacious lodge comfortably sleeps up to 13 guests (12 adults and 1 child) and offers six thoughtfully designed bedrooms across multiple levels, providing both privacy and togetherness for larger groups. The sleeping layout includes a king bedroom with private bath and deck access on the entry level, a queen bedroom upstairs, a king bedroom accessed through the game room, a large bunk room with two twin bunk sets and a queen bed, a full bedroom on the top level, and a king bedroom on the basement level. Streaming TVs are available throughout the home for added comfort and convenience.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Guests enjoy three full bathrooms, including a private en-suite and two hallway baths, ensuring ease and functionality for groups of all sizes. With parking for up to five vehicles and accommodations for up to two pets with an additional fee, Luxury Lodge is designed to meet every need.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Upon entering the home, you&amp;rsquo;re greeted by a stunning great room featuring vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors, and expansive windows that fill the space with natural light. Plush leather seating surrounds a dramatic stone gas fireplace, creating the perfect setting to relax, unwind, and enjoy mountain views. The open-concept layout flows seamlessly into a beautifully appointed kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a fully stocked setup ideal for preparing group meals. A formal dining table seats eight, complemented by additional breakfast bar seating for seven.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Entertainment awaits on multiple levels, highlighted by a dedicated game room featuring a full-size pool table, arcade and board games, and stylish lounge seating. Outdoors, the private deck offers a true alpine experience with a propane BBQ grill and a secluded hot tub tucked beneath the pines, perfect for soaking after a day of adventure.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Luxury Lodge Estate offers a rare combination of space, comfort, walkable location, and high-end amenities. Whether visiting for a weekend escape, family gathering, or extended stay, this exceptional Big Bear home delivers a memorable mountain experience in every season.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
