&lt;br /&gt;
Splash Mountain is your next vacation destination from heaven!! This amazing newly renovated Big Bear home will no doubt be your best vacation yet. Situated on a beautifully manicured lot, you have a large grassy side yard for playing and outdoor summer activities. A rare find in Big Bear, your family will love the amenities this home has to offer.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Upon entry you will immediately note the extensive upgrades and renovations made by our owners, like an EV charger (at no charge), fresh paint from the gorgeous hardwood flooring to the high vaulted mountain style ceilings pairs perfectly with toasty fireplaces, new appliances, and the ultimate game room loft to provide the most amazing atmosphere for your next vacation to Big Bear!&amp;nbsp;Enter into the great room, a wonderful place for friends and family to gather and enjoy each other&amp;#39;s company. Snuggle up on the plush couches to enjoy the toasty wood burning fireplace and enjoy a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI provided. The big open windows offer the perfect amount of natural lighting, and a player piano also sits here if you would like to play a tune or two. Around the corner you will be graced with a second family room boasting additional sitting couches paired with massive windows and an added Streaming TV and fireplace, there is a spot for everyone here at Splash Mountain! The formal dining room continues on this main level, boasting a formal dining table with ample seating for a group of eight paired with big open windows allowing forested views while dining.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The chef of your group will absolutely love the gourmet kitchen boasting pine cabinets stocked with all that you need for preparing your home cooked meals. Cookware and appliances, even a dishwasher is on hand to make group meals a breeze. Additional breakfast bar seating is also available at the breakfast island ensuring group meals can be enjoyed together at once. This lower main entry level of your chalet hosts two of your sleeping quarters and two of your bathrooms, one of which is the spacious primary suite, complete with its own fireplace and private ensuite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms and a hallway bathroom are located on the upstairs second level, all of which are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, and fresh shower towels. You will absolutely love the upstairs game room loft, packed full of fun and entertainment you will find a full-size pool table and foosball available to keep the group entertained. This will be where the group spends your nights challenging each other at a game of billiards. Venturing out to the back deck area you will find wonderful patio furnishings and a propane BBQ available for your use. The highlight of this property is the private yard boasting an enclosed gazebo for outdoor dining and a private in-deck hot tub under the stars where you will love soaking your muscles. Just blocks from Big Bear Village your group will love this central location keeping you within minutes to local activities, shopping, and delicious dining.&lt;br /&gt;
