&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Bohemia Big Bear! This amazing single level chalet home is perfect for a group of friends or family getaway to the mountains- ideally located in central Big Bear Lake only a few minutes from the Village where you can enjoy a lovely walk, movie, or dinner. You&amp;#39;ll have the comforts from home along with an amazing year round location to ensure a memorable and relaxing vacation can be had here including a cozy and relaxing chalet under the stars and a ping-pong table in the game room converted garage- the possibilities are endless from here!&lt;br /&gt;
