Enter your home in the cozy and warm living room where you are greeted with beautiful hardwood floors, knotty pine ceilings, and big open windows that provide the perfect balance of natural lighting and forest views of the cute neighborhood outside. Snuggle up on the cozy couches as you warm your toes together in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace and pop on a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining a dinner party or hosting your next family holiday in the mountains as it leads seamlessly to the equipped dining area and kitchen where you will find plenty of sitting space for your meals together between the breakfast bar stools and sitting table. The cute kitchen offers oak cabinets stocked with cookware and utensils along with stainless appliances and a dishwasher for a quick and easy cleanup.&lt;br /&gt;
