&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Moonlight Ridge! This adorable single level cozy cabin is the perfect destination for a small family or group of friends to head to the mountains and enjoy a memorable and relaxing vacation to Big Bear. Perfectly nestled in the trees of this quiet Moonridge neighborhood your group will have quick and convenient access to all local activities while being especially close to Bear Mountain Resort for skiing, golf, and the local Alpine Zoo right at your fingertips. Furnished with all that you need for the ultimate vacation experience you will love your stay here!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter your chalet to be met with a light and bright open floor plan boasting gorgeous hardwood floors and knotty pine beamed ceilings that pair perfectly with the big open windows providing you with the perfect balance of natural lighting and great views of the snow falling outside. You will love snuggling up here on the cozy couch as you warm your toes together in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace and enjoy a movie on the mounted flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) Around the corner here the chef of your group will love and appreciate the open and equipped kitchen and dining areas that are perfectly stocked with all that you need to host your next family holiday or prepare home cooked meals and slope side snacks for your day. Oak cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils for your use along with general appliances and a dishwasher plus the breakfast island barstools pair up with the log dining nook to ensure your party has plenty of comfortable seating to enjoy your meals together.&lt;br /&gt;
