property.description:
Wolf Cub Cabin&amp;nbsp;| Resort Cozy Cabin w/ Hot Tub&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Fall in love with Wolf Cub Cabin, our furnished and ultra cozy two-story vintage Gambrel has been fully renovated and updated with your vacation experience in mind ensuring the most memorable of stays can be had here, perfect for a couples getaway, group of friends, or even a small family to enjoy. Located just below Bear Mountain Resort you will have quick and easy access to local hiking trails, winter time ski lifts, and summer time tee time at the golf course or driving range as each is within a mile of your cabin&amp;#39;s central location. Boasting the comforts from home paired with modern amenities and added bonuses throughout your group will love your visit here at Wolf Cub Cabin!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Moonridge is a fantastic year round location but does require 4X4 with snow chains in the winter months due to the incline of this road however you truly have the very best of Big Bear at your fingertips here including the newly built Alpine Zoo and upcoming Corridor set to open in the next couple of years featuring shops and dining along Moonridge Road which is sure to be a hit! You&amp;#39;ll enter your chalet on the lower level in the cozy living room through massive sliding glass doors that add to your nature and birdwatching abilities as well as beautiful snowfall in the winter months. Comfy sitting couches and chairs are sat around a toasty wood burning fireplace and mounted flat screen TV with Cable and complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment. You will love lounging here and taking in the beautiful knotty pine wall accents and beamed cabin ceiling. Gorgeous hardwood floors and central forced heat keeps your group comfortable no matter the season you choose to visit while the necessities and essentials are right on hand! A cute dining table and equipped kitchen around the corner here offers all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals right here from the cabin. Enjoy the freshly painted modern kitchen with cabinets stocked with cookware and utensils plus general appliances are available to easily make memorable meals for your stay. You also gain access from here out to your rear deck which is definitely the spot where you will spend most of your time while you are here, offering a propane BBQ and beautiful outdoor dining furnishings overlooking the national forest along with added bonus amenities.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy relaxing around the propane firepit or take a nice soak under a million stars in your own private hot tub here, this is the perfect spot for unwinding in the evenings and relaxing after a fun day of adventures out on the lake or mountain. You&amp;#39;ll love the spacious full bathroom here on the lower entry level which offers beautiful wood accent walls and modern fixtures plus a unique half bath is also available upstairs in the master bedroom. Both of your spacious sleeping quarters are on the upstairs level of your chalet where the gorgeous wood wall accents and mountain themed d&amp;eacute;cor continues, each room is made up for your group&amp;#39;s arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive. You will love the master suite offering a private balcony with sitting chairs for you to enjoy sipping your first cup of coffee in the mornings and a TV w/ Cable. Wolf Cub Cabin has it all- pairing the comforts from home with modern features and added amenities plus a prime central location to ensure a memorable and exciting vacation to the mountains is in store. You will love your stay here!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Queen Bed, TV w/ Cable, Private Half Bath, Deck Access -Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: Full Bed- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath- Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Private Half Bath- Bedroom 1- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
-Sleeps 4&lt;br /&gt;
-2 Cars Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
-2 Pets Welcome w/ Additional Fee&lt;br /&gt;
-896 Total Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
