&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Cienega Getaway!! Our fully furnished and equipped Boulder Bay townhouse condo is the perfect destination for a group of friends or family vacation to the mountains to experience all that Big Bear has to offer. Located walking distance to the lake or local marina and under ten minutes by car to local activities, this complex offers a prime year round location no matter the season you choose to visit however summertime tennis courts, outdoor pool, and community hot tub are just a few of guests favorite key offerings.&lt;br /&gt;
