Enter into the lower level living room area where you are greeted with beautiful hardwood floors, beamed cathedral ceilings, and the big open sliding glass window that provides the perfect balance of natural lighting and views of the complex meadow and snow falling outside. Snuggle up here on the comfy couch together as you enjoy warming your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace as you pop on a movie on the mounted flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) The breakfast bat stools pair perfectly with the formal log dining table to ensure you have plenty of comfortable sitting space for your group to enjoy your meals together right here at the condo. Your chef will love the equipped and modern kitchen offering all that you need to prepare home cooked meals and holiday feasts including oak cabinets stocked with cookware and utensils, general appliances, and even a dishwasher for a quick and easy cleanup.&lt;br /&gt;
