Boasting two spacious levels of living space you will love having a bathroom on each level of your chalet along with one entry level bedroom and two upstairs bedrooms, each offers big open windows and is made up for your arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your vacation stay. Outside you have a private patio area with cozy outdoor furnishings and a propane BBQ so you can relax in the evenings and grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake. Take a quick stroll down to local Pleasure Point Marina or hop in the car and you are within a short ten minute drive to all local activities- the possibilities are endless from here!&lt;br /&gt;
