Cozy Haven Cottage in Big Bear Lake&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bring the family or a group of friends to enjoy your very own mountain top &amp;quot;Cozy Haven&amp;quot; while experiencing the perfect getaway in the mountains at Big Bear here in our ultra cozy and central retreat. Located in the Moonridge area your group will be within minutes to the Bear Mountain Resort, meaning you will have year round activities at your fingertips including skiing, golf, hiking, and the local Alpine Zoo.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter in on the lower level of your chalet where you are greeted with the coziest open floor plan living room area that features knotty pine cathedral ceilings paired with big open windows to take in the wonderful mountain views and falling snow outside in the winter. Enjoy cuddling up on the comfy couches around the cozy wood burning fireplace while enjoying your favorite movie on the Streaming TV with digital services (must have your own log ins for Netflix, Hulu, etc) and complimentary hi speed WIFI provided by the owners for your convenience. The spacious open floor plan leads right to the adorable dining room area where you will find a formal log dining table for six that pairs perfectly with the breakfast bar stools to ensure there is ample sitting options available for your group. The wonderful chef&amp;#39;s kitchen offers great counter spaces paired with oak cabinets stocked full with all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals including cookware, utensils, and general appliances including a dishwasher to make your meals here a breeze!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Boasting a spacious sleeping quarter and full bathroom on each level this chalet offers the perfect amount of space to keep everyone connected while still providing privacy and comfort, all are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh towels for your visit. You will love the private balcony from the upstairs master suite, this is the perfect spot to sip your first cup of coffee among the birds in the mornings. Both bedrooms offer sliding glass doors to the great alpine forest outside while the lower level bedroom is perfect for the kids with an added bunk bed setup. Venturing outside you will love the relaxing front sun deck with sitting chairs and wonderful mountain and forest views, you will love unwinding here in the evenings. Off of the lower level bedroom is an added private sun deck overlooking the backyard, you will love this patio setting with outdoor furnishings and a propane BBQ for you to grill up dinner and spend your evenings under the stars.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
