&lt;strong&gt;Bear Cabin on the Green | Walk to Golf and Ski Lift&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perched along the edge of the Bear Mountain 9-hole Golf Course and just moments from the ski lifts, Bear Cabin on the Green delivers an exhilarating alpine getaway with expansive golf-course and mountain views in every direction. Please note that &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;the kitchen features a high-capacity countertop toaster oven in place of a traditional full oven&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, thoughtfully equipped to support easy meal prep throughout your stay. With tee-times practically in your backyard and the ski lift an easy walk away, this home offers unbeatable access to year-round adventure at Bear Mountain Resort.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for families and group gatherings, the property includes a separate guest apartment above the garage with its own private entrance. This cozy bonus space adds extra sleeping room, a convenient kitchenette for quick snacks, and a game table for additional entertainment. In the main house, the open-concept layout connects the welcoming living room to the well-equipped kitchen, offering everything you need for breakfast spreads, apr&amp;egrave;s-ski bites, and relaxed vacation cooking. A dishwasher, full cookware set, and the large countertop toaster oven ensure meal preparation is simple and efficient. Gather around the breakfast bar or the spacious log dining table for shared meals and conversations. A dedicated laundry area with washer and dryer adds year-round convenience.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The inviting living room features comfortable seating around an electric fireplace, high-speed Wi-Fi, and cable TV for cozy nights in. Upstairs, you&amp;rsquo;ll find restful bedrooms with private balconies showcasing beautiful golf-course and mountain views. Fresh linens, blankets, pillows, and towels are provided to make your stay comfortable and worry-free.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step outside to enjoy the expansive fenced backyard, wraparound redwood decks, and brand-new propane BBQ, ideal for scenic outdoor grilling. Guests will also love the game room space, kids&amp;rsquo; playground, and bocce ball field, making this cabin a fantastic choice for all-ages fun and all-day relaxation.&lt;br /&gt;
Blending a premier location with thoughtful amenities and breathtaking views, Bear Cabin on the Green offers the perfect year-round Big Bear retreat&amp;mdash;full of comfort, adventure, and unforgettable mountain charm.&lt;br /&gt;
