&lt;br /&gt;
Moose Manor&amp;nbsp;is a truly spectacular vacation home, centrally located in the heart of Big Bear Lake, packed from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind, and boasting comfortable furnishings for a group to enjoy your stay together. You will absolutely love the open floor and mountain ski lodge vibes the moment you enter your home, featuring radiant floors, central forced heat, a tankless water heater, washer and dryer, wine bar and gorgeous open windows in every room, the natural lighting makes snow days so much fun here! Soak up your day of adventure in your private hot tub under the stars, or challenge the group at a game of pool or ping pong inside or head out back to enjoy your very own on site mini putt-putt golf setup!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The cozy living room offers all that you need for a memorable gathering space here in the mountain. Vaulted cathedral beamed ceilings pair with gorgeous hardwood floors and the perfect amount of natural lighting from the many open windows throughout your chalet. Snuggle up on the leather couches which are perfectly sat around the gas faux log rock fireplace and mounted flat screen TV with Cable and complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment, this is the perfect spot for snuggling up and enjoying a movie night together as you warm your toes in front of the fire. The open floor plan leads to the open game room area with a full size billiards table for your group to challenge each other at a fun game of billiards while you enjoy your time together. A separate dining room area and multi-functional breakfast bar pair together to provide ample sitting areas for a large group to make memories over meals. The chef of your group will love the fully stocked kitchen complete with all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals or entertain a dinner party right here at the cabin. Oak cabinets are stocked full with cookware and utensils for your use while ample counter space and general appliances including a dishwasher ensures that your cleanup here at Moose Manor is a breeze! You will love the adorable wet bar and wine fridge for your adult beverages plus a stacked washer and dryer is on hand for an added convenience for those wet snow clothes or extended vacation stays.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Your property is two stories and fully furnished with easy and convenient access to all of your sleeping quarters on the upstairs second level including two spacious primary suites with amazing private bathrooms. All of your quarters are made up for your group with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive for your vacation.&amp;nbsp;Venture outside to find the most relaxing and serene private estate available for you complete with new decking and outdoor patio furnishings for you to enjoy grilling up your freshly caught dinner on the propane BBQ. The outdoor fireplace and private hot tub under the stars is where you will love spending your time unwinding in the evenings. For even more fun there is a mini putting green for the golf enthusiasts plus a half size basketball court for your group to enjoy within your fully fenced complex.&lt;br /&gt;
