&lt;br /&gt;
Whiskey Mountain Lodge is the perfect escape cabin for a family reunion or group of friends to enjoy the best of Big Bear together in relaxation and comfort. Located in a quiet tree lined Sugarloaf neighborhood your group will be conveniently located within a ten minute drive to all local activities including the lake and ski resorts. Boasting modern d&amp;eacute;cor and amenities with your group&amp;#39;s vacation stay in mind you will have all that you need right at your fingertips here. This spacious corner lot offers easy access and ample flat parking no matter the season you choose to visit the mountains plus expansive wrapped sun decks and outdoor furnishings to ensure relaxation and serenity are priority for your stay.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
