&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to The Big Bear Fox Lodge! Your dream vacation awaits at this spacious, fully furnished retreat in Bear City. Nestled in the peaceful &amp;quot;Poet&amp;#39;s Corner&amp;quot; neighborhood, you&amp;#39;re just a short 10-minute drive from downtown Village, ski resorts, and marinas. This home is the ultimate getaway, with its impressive indoor pool, hot tub, and game room offering endless entertainment for everyone.&lt;br /&gt;
