&lt;br /&gt;
Get ready to fall in love with our mountain-style retreat, where nature meets comfort in the most delightful way! Just minutes from the sparkling Big Bear Lake and the charming downtown Village, this freshly renovated, multi-level haven is the perfect spot for your next getaway.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Tucked among the trees, you&amp;rsquo;ll instantly feel the tranquility of this cozy escape. Kick back in the living room, where comfy couches surround a beautiful stone fireplace&amp;mdash;ideal for movie nights on the big screen Streaming TV. The kitchen is a dream for any chef, with stainless steel appliances, elegant tile countertops, and plenty of light to inspire your culinary creations. And don&amp;rsquo;t forget the upper rear deck&amp;mdash;perfect for summer evenings with its stylish patio furniture, gas fire pit, and fantastic BBQ area.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The fun doesn&amp;rsquo;t stop there! Gather around the gorgeous dining table in the formal dining room, or challenge the family to a friendly game of shuffleboard in the foyer. Planning a longer stay? We&amp;rsquo;ve got you covered with a separate laundry room featuring a stacked washer and dryer.&lt;br /&gt;
