&lt;br /&gt;
Treetop Views pairs a mountainous alpine environment steps to the National Forest and the best of Big Bear while freshly furnished from head to toe with all that guests need for a memorable and entertaining vacation to the mountains. This hillside gem is centrally located in upper Moonridge, just minutes from the newly renovated Alpine Zoo and Bear Mountain Golf and Ski Resort providing you with quick access to year round activities plus boasts the perfect sledding hill right on the property in the winter season.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
After trekking the two flights of stairs to enter your chalet you are greeted with a cozy entry level living room, boasting ultra comfortable sitting couches around a toasty rock fireplace and Streaming TV, this is the perfect spot for snuggling up and watching a movie or the snow falling thru the big open picture windows.&amp;nbsp; For added entertainment your group will find a full size pool table to enjoy a game of billiards within this spacious open floor plan. The chef of your group will absolutely love the renovated kitchen, boasting all that you need for whipping up your home cooked meals including granite counters, new stainless appliances and cookware, plus the dining area offers a log table for six to enjoy your meals together. For your convenience this downstairs entry level boasts a separate laundry area with a washer and dryer as well as a shared hallway full bath. Upstairs you will find your three sleeping quarters including the spacious master suite with it&amp;#39;s own private balcony and fireplace, all are made up for your stay with warm blankets and fresh towels.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Venturing outside you will love the wrap-around decks under a blanket of pine trees and a peaceful and relaxing forested neighborhood, this is the perfect spot for sipping your first cup of coffee in the mornings or unwinding after a long day of adventures on the mountain. Boasting all that you need for a memorable and exciting vacation to Big Bear you will absolutely love your stay here at Treetop Views, pairing a prime convenient location with the necessities from home, don&amp;#39;t miss your chance to book your next home away from home today!&lt;br /&gt;
