property.description:
Eagle Point Lodge&amp;nbsp;| Hot Tub- Game Room- Central&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Grab the family or a group of friends and head up to Big Bear to experience Eagle Point Lodge, our freshly renovated and fully furnished downtown chalet has all that you need for a relaxing and memorable vacation to the mountains. Enjoy rustic modern amenities and sprawling spaces for the group to enjoy your time together, the spacious game room and loft provide the perfect spot to unwind and relax with game tables and a private hot tub, you may never want to leave! Located in the highly desirable &amp;quot;Eagle Point&amp;quot; neighborhood your group will be within a short walk to the lake or Village shops for dining and entertainment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Our unique level entry home offer ample year round parking and easy access, situated on a quiet corner lot with a big open front yard you will love your stay here! Entering into the foyer which flows seamlessly into the living/dining/kitchen spaces you are immediately greeted with log accents and knotty pine beamed ceilings. The cozy living room offers sitting couches in front of a toasty wood burning fireplace. Snuggle up with a loved one while watching the snow fall through the big open windows.&amp;nbsp;Enjoy your home cooked meals together at the custom log dining table for eight or grab a stool at the adorable breakfast bar, the seating arrangements are ample here! Premium granite counter tops pair perfectly with the oak cabinets in the chef&amp;#39;s kitchen, stocked full with your cookware and utensils for meals. Stainless steel appliances and even a dishwasher ensure that your home cooked meals here are a breeze!! A separate laundry room area with a washer and dryer plus a guest half bath here also adds convenience for those wet snow clothes or long term stays. A guest bedroom and full bathroom are also conveniently located here on this lower entry level for easy access.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Venture up the grand staircase to find a spacious open loft, perfect for hanging out on a snowy day your group can enjoy added sitting couches and a mounted flat screen paired with a full size pool table to challenge each other at a game of billiards. You will find the rest of your comfortable sleeping quarters and remaining bathrooms here on the upstairs level, each is made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and shower towels. Enjoy modern flat screen TVs, private bathrooms, and outdoor balcony areas from each room, a foosball table is also an added bonus to the kids bunk room while the charm and custom accents are plentiful here! Outside you will find ample wrapped sun decks providing wonderful spaces to sit and enjoy the beautiful alpine outside, outdoor patio chairs and furnishings sit on each level of this massive deck. A private backyard area offers a wonderful patio with a propane BBQ to grill up dinner. Enjoy a soak in your own private hot tub under the stars after a long day of adventure out on the mountain. The attached garage has also been converted to a fun game room area with an added bunk bed set and game tables to keep your whole group entertained year round! Eagle Point Lodge truly has it all- pairing the ultimate convenience in location with modern amenities and true mountain charm, you will love your visit here with us!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Full Bed + Twin Bed, TV, Patio Access- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: King Bed, TV, Private 3/4 Bath, Balcony Access- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3: Queen Bed, Private Full Bath- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 4: Twin/Twin Bunk Set, Deck Access, Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
