Majestic Sky Modern Resort Retreat&amp;nbsp;| Hot Tub &amp;amp; Games&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Majestic Sky Retreat is the ultimate vacation home experience for any group or family vacation together, pairing the comforts from home with high end modern upgrades and a prime Snow Summit ski and bike park resort location. Sitting on a quiet lot just below the resort you will be within a quick stroll to the ski lifts and under five minutes in the car to the lake, Village shops, and grocery stores. Our beautiful newly renovated home boasts necessities paired with fun and entertaining games and relaxing amenities to ensure a memorable experience can be had.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter into a grand family room area with vaulted cathedral ceilings, new carpet, and ultra comfortable furnishings for your group to enjoy your time together. Snuggle up on the over sized plush couch and watch a movie on the mounted flat screen TV in front of a toasty fire in the faux log gas fireplace. Take on the group at a game of foosball or shuffleboard as the open floor plan leads you right to the game room areas. The well appointed chef&amp;#39;s kitchen offers you all that you need for your home cooked meals together. Gorgeous marble counter tops pair perfectly with the new stainless appliances and the stocked oak cabinets to provide you with all that you need. Cookware, utensils, and a dishwasher make your meals here a breeze! Breakfast bar stools pair perfectly with the massive dining table to ensure you can sit and enjoy meals together as a large group.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
All three bedrooms and both baths are easily accessible here in our spacious single level chalet, all are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels. A separate washer and dryer in the laundry room ensures that you can conveniently keep up with those wet snow clothes or extended stays here as well! Venture outside to find an amazing fully fenced and pet friendly property, wrapped sun decks and outdoor patio furnishings offer you a great space to enjoy your visit. A propane BBQ and outdoor seating make for a great area to hang out and make memories! Enjoy taking a soak in the brand new hot tub under the stars after a fun day of adventures out on the mountain or lake! Majestic Sky Retreat truly has it all- pairing the ultimate comforts from home with added fun and bonus relaxation this home won&amp;#39;t disappoint no matter the season you choose to visit! This prime location gives your group the very best of Big Bear at your fingertips! Don&amp;#39;t miss your chance to book this amazing chalet today!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
