property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Mockingbird Family Getaway&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;Hot Tub -&amp;nbsp; Walk to Lake&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Mockingbird Getaway is the perfect mountain retreat for those looking to enjoy Big Bear with a more modern touch and feel. Our fully furnished two story chalet has been freshly renovated from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind, boasting fine amenities and modern d&amp;eacute;cor to provide your group with all that you need for a memorable and relaxing alpine vacation. Enjoy hours of entertainment on the game tables or soak those muscles after a fun day on the mountain in either the jetted spa tub or the new private hot tub out back, you will love relaxing here as you look for shooting stars. Centrally located within a short walk to Snow Summit Resort or Big Bear Lake you have local activities right at your fingertips from here!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter into a grand foyer with beautiful tile floors, freshly painted walls, and the custom wrought iron staircase immediately catching your eyes as you set down your gear or take off those wet snow clothes. The ultra cozy living room area is here offering beautiful hardwood floors and a comfortable plush sitting couches sat perfectly in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace. Enjoy watching a movie here on the massive mounted flat screen Streaming TV or watching the snow falling outside thru the big open windows. Complimentary WIFI is provided for your enjoyment however guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services. Around the corner your group will find the formal dining room offering a wonderful space to sit together as a group and enjoy meals or entertain a dinner party. The chef of your group will absolutely love the beautifully renovated kitchen area, boasting tile floors and marble counter tops for your meal preparations. Oak cabinets are stocked full with your utensils and cookware while general appliances and a dishwasher ensures that your cleanup is a breeze!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
