property.description:
Pinewood Inn&amp;nbsp;| Cozy Modern Cabin w/ Hot Tub&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Pinewood Inn is perfect for those looking to experience a relaxing and comfortable mountain vacation experience at Big Bear. Perfectly situated in a prime central Moonridge location you will be within minutes to all local activities while having the comforts from home available to you. Utilize the chef&amp;#39;s kitchen and dining areas for your home cooked meals together or enjoy a relaxing evening out on the patio with a your own private hot tub under the stars.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You will love this spacious gambrel style two story home, featuring an open floor plan on the lower entry level perfect for entertaining your family, group of friends, or even a small dinner party. Hardwood floors pair with the knotty pine beamed ceilings and cozy sitting couches which are perfectly sat around the native rock fireplace to set the ambience and provide you with a great space to snuggle up and watch a movie on the mounted flat screen Streaming TV in front of a toasty fire as you warm your toes and watch the snow falling outside. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) The adorable breakfast bar offers stool seats plus the log dining table ensure ample seating options are available for your group meals together. Ample counter spaces are paired with the freshly painted oak cabinets which are stocked with cookware and utensils for your meal preparations. Newer stainless appliances including a dishwasher are added for your convenience while a stacked washer and dryer in the lower level guest bath is available for those wet snow clothes or extended stays.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Venturing upstairs to the second level you will find your two spacious sleeping quarters and an additional guest bath, all are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive and each room offers a Streaming TV for your added convenience. As you head out back the the great outdoors you will find a spacious and fenced property that offers an amazing sun deck. Enjoy the outdoor patio furnishings, propane BBQ, and your own private hot tub to take a soak under the stars after a day of adventures out on the mountain. The side and front decks also offer sitting chairs and a wonderful space for you to sip your first cup of coffee in the mornings among the birds. Pinewood Inn is a fantastic vacation choice for any group no matter the season, fully furnished with all that you need for a memorable and relaxing trip to Big Bear, you can&amp;#39;t beat this incredible location! Don&amp;#39;t miss your opportunity to enjoy this chalet for your next alpine vacation!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: King Bed, Streaming TV&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: Two Twin/Twin Bunks + Twin Trundle Under, Streaming TV&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
