&lt;br /&gt;
Step into the enchanting Pinglewood Cabin, where the serenity of a quiet Fawnskin neighborhood meets the thrill of Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s outdoor adventures! Nestled in a secluded spot, this charming chalet is the perfect retreat for your group getaway. Just minutes away from off-roading, biking, and hiking trails, and only a short ten-minute drive across the lake to Big Bear, you&amp;rsquo;ll enjoy peace and excitement equally.&lt;br /&gt;
