&lt;br /&gt;
Looking to experience the ultimate Big Bear vacation right from the shoreline!? Cove Lakefront Chalet is the perfect vacation home for just that! Sitting on the shoreline in the quiet Boulder Bay neighborhood of the valley, your group will have an abundance of activities right at your fingertips while still within a ten-minute car ride to the ski resorts or downtown Village shops. Sprawling in fully furnished spaces for your group to enjoy our two-story home has all that you need for a memorable visit to the mountains including entertaining games, kitchen essentials, and a new private hot tub under the stars!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
