Enter into a grand living room area upon entry with vaulted knotty pine cathedral ceilings and soaring picture windows to take in the panoramic lake views surrounding you. Comfortable sitting couches offer great spaces to sit and make memories around a toasty rock wood-burning fireplace. Enjoy your favorite movie on the massive flat-screen Streaming TV or just snuggle up and watch the snow falling outside. (Guests must have their own accounts to use Streaming services.) There are two separate lake view dining areas that each offer a custom formal log dining table for your group or holiday meals together along with deck access and more fantastic lake views. The breakfast bar pairs stool seats and gorgeous granite countertops for your chef to prepare your home-cooked meals. The oak cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils for your convenience while general appliances and a dishwasher ensure that your meals are a breeze here!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Head downstairs to the cozy family room for more added fun where you will find sitting couches around one more natural wood fireplace and another huge TV. Enjoy a game of pool on the full-size billiards table, foosball table, arcade basketball, or just watch all the action from the mini bar. This is a great space to make wonderful memories together.&amp;nbsp;A separate laundry room area offers a washer and dryer for your extended stays or wet snow clothes to keep things convenient. All four bedrooms and bathrooms are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels plus offer deck views.&amp;nbsp;Venture outside to enjoy the expansive wrapped sun decks and expansive lakefront property with a seasonal boat dock. (Water levels pending access) Enjoying grilling up your freshly caught dinner on the natural gas BBQ as you enjoy the patio furnishings or take a soak in the new private hot tub under the stars as you unwind after a fun day of adventures out on the lake. Cove Lakefront Chalet truly has it all ensuring groups and families have the very best of Big Bear at their fingertips our furnished mountain chalet has all that you need for a memorable and relaxing lakeside vacation. Don&amp;#39;t miss your chance to book this spectacular chalet for your upcoming mountain vacation today!&lt;br /&gt;
