&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Crestwood Summit!! Perfect for a family vacation or group of friends looking to enjoy the very best of Big Bear for their next vacation our cozy single level chalet cabin sits just below Snow Summit Resort for quick and convenient year-round access to winter ski lifts, snow tubing, summertime scenic sky chair hikes, and the bike park. Packed with the necessities for a great vacation along with modern comforts and a pool table for entertainment your group will absolutely love this cabin!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Entering your home, you are greeted with beautiful hardwood floors, freshly painted walls, big open windows, new carpet, and plenty of space for your group to sprawl out and enjoy your time together with double living and family rooms available. To the right is your cozy living room area which offers you comfy couches where you can snuggle up and warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace as you pop on a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided by the owners for your enjoyment. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) Around the corner to the left is your second family room which boasts even more cozy sitting couches and a regulation size pool table so you can keep the crew entertained for hours right here at the cabin.&amp;nbsp;Both of your family and living room areas connect conveniently to the dining room and kitchen which is perfect for entertaining a dinner party or hosting your next holiday meal in the mountains as you can stay connected with the group while you prepare your feasts. Breakfast bar stools pair with the bistro style table to ensure your whole group can sit together comfortably and enjoy your home cooked meals. The chef in your group will love the cute kitchen offering all that you need to prepare snacks for the slopes as the oak cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils plus general appliances and a dishwasher is on hand to ensure your cleanup is a breeze.&lt;br /&gt;
