&lt;br /&gt;
Step outside to experience the exceptional lakeside property, featuring great patio spaces and a propane BBQ perfect for grilling up your freshly caught dinner from the lake. Unwind in the private bay-side yard under a million stars, soaking away the day&amp;#39;s adventures. With a seasonal boat dock (water levels pending) for summer activities, Lakeview Getaway truly has it all. Make this your home away from home in the mountains and live your vacation dreams today!&lt;br /&gt;
