&lt;br /&gt;
Walk straight to the slopes. Enjoy breathtaking mountain views. Stay in one of the most convenient locations in all of Big Bear.&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Switzerland Slopes, a cozy yet modern townhouse chalet located steps from Snow Summit Ski Resort and Bike Park. This four-season retreat blends comfort, style, and location, giving guests the ultimate Big Bear experience.&amp;nbsp;No parking. No shuttles. No stress.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
