Silver Tip Chalet&amp;nbsp;| Resort Log Cabin- Game Tables&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Silver Tip Chalet lives up to it&amp;#39;s name from the moment you arrive to your&amp;nbsp;log cabin masterpiece in the mountains- this incredible chalet offers unbeatable panoramic valley and ski slope views from the amazing sun deck and is packed from head to toe with your vacation stay experience in mind. Freshly renovated and furnished with incredible custom log work throughout your group will absolutely love your stay here! Located within a quick drive to Bear Mountain Resort your group will have the best of Big Bear right at your fingertips here.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter your home and you are immediately greeted with gorgeous hardwood floors, knotty pine cathedral ceilings, and massive floor to ceiling windows that provide the perfect balance of natural lighting and amazing views- your group will feel as if you have your own mountain lodge to yourselves for your trip. Enter into your cozy and warm living room area with plush sitting couches where you can snuggle up and warm your toes in front of the toasty fireplace as you pop on a movie on the mounted flat screen Streaming TV. The attached family room also offers added sitting couches and relaxing spaces to enjoy your visit together. The open space floor plan leads right into the beautiful kitchen and dining areas which are perfect for entertaining a dinner party or hosting your next family holiday feast as you can prepare as you entertain and stay connected with everyone.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The formal dining room offers a custom log sitting table and chairs that pair perfectly with the breakfast bar stools to ensure everyone has a comfortable space to enjoy your meals together as a group. The chef of your group will fall in love with this gourmet kitchen-&amp;nbsp;the oak cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils for your use along with granite counters, stainless appliances, and even a dishwasher to ensure your cleanup is just as easy.&amp;nbsp;You will love having quick and easy access to your three bedrooms and bathrooms, each room is made up for your group with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive for your vacation. Outside the amazing sun deck offers patio furnishings, a propane BBQ for your grilling pleasure, and the best spot in Big Bear to watch for shooting stars! You&amp;#39;ll love sitting among the treetops and taking in the incredible valley and ski slope views from your deck as you sip your fist cup of coffee in the mornings before heading out for adventures.&lt;br /&gt;
