property.description:
The Alps Lodge&amp;nbsp;| Central Log Cabin Retreat&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The Alps Lodge is the perfect four-season destination for any group visiting Big Bear, you will have all that you need for a memorable and relaxing visit to the mountains. Our single-story log cabin is the perfect escape for your trip, boasting ultra-modern and comfortable furnishings paired with added relaxation and serenity. The spacious tree-lined central lot sits within a short walk from Lake or a quick drive to the ski slopes or downtown Village area for shopping and dining.&amp;nbsp; Also features a fully fenced yard providing security and privacy for the kids or Fido.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Boasting modern amenities and furnishings you will feel as if you have your own private lodge to yourselves the moment you enter into the warm and relaxing family room area, forced central heat keeps your group cozy no matter the season you choose to visit while the beautiful hardwood floors pair perfectly with the knotty pine vaulted ceilings. You will love the comfortable sitting couches sat in front of the toasty easy to light fireplace, with a flat-screen streaming TV, and complimentary WIFI provided for your convenience, this is the perfect space to snuggle up in front of the fire and enjoy a movie night or watch the snow fall through the big open windows. The awesome open floor plan allows the chef of your group to visit with your family and friends while whipping up your home-cooked meals in the updated kitchen, the oak cabinets are stocked full with all that you will need including cookware and utensils. General appliances and even a dishwasher are available for your convenience making your meal prep and cleanup here a breeze. A breakfast nook bar is a great place for enjoying meals or drinks, and there is a game/dining table in a separate sunroom with its own wood-burning fireplace to keep you toasty as the snow falls all around you outside.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
All three of your sleeping quarters are made up for your vacation with warm linens, blankets, and fresh shower towels in each bathroom. You will love the spacious master suite which offers an open full bathroom and flat-screen streaming TV.&amp;nbsp; The two other guest rooms boast terrific views of the meadows and mountains. Venture out from the dining room area to find the spacious back sun deck and fenced back yard, boasting outdoor patio furnishings and a fire pit for your enjoyment. You will love relaxing here or firing up the propane BBQ after a day of adventures out on the mountain and enjoying the peaceful, beautiful views.&amp;nbsp; It is the perfect spot for sipping your first cup of coffee in the mornings among the birds. The Alps Lodge has it all pairing the comforts from home with modern cabin d&amp;eacute;cor and bonus amenities plus a prime central location, this cabin is the ultimate destination for your next mountain vacation! Don&amp;#39;t miss your chance at the vacation of a lifetime by booking this chalet for your next alpine vacation to Big Bear!!&lt;br /&gt;
