&lt;br /&gt;
3 Bears Inn is a beautiful log-style cabin situated in the tranquil area of Moonridge, meaning this home is within close proximity to Bear Mountain Ski Resort, Big Bear Golf Course, and the newly renovated local Alpine Zoo. You will absolutely love this luxury chalet- furnished from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind you will enjoy the open floor plan with vaulted knotty pine ceilings along with the fresh marble countertops paired with stainless steel appliances in the kitchen.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Upon entering this beautiful cabin is a spacious living room, perfect for family gatherings or a movie night.&amp;nbsp; With the cozy wood-burning fireplace and 65&amp;quot; flat-screen Smart TV paired with the huge sectional couch make for the perfect place for cuddling up and watching the snow fall or enjoying a movie. The open floor plan from the living room to the dining room and into the kitchen makes it easy to enjoy the whole group&amp;#39;s company.&amp;nbsp; The kitchen is freshly equipped with all that you need for preparing home-cooked meals or entertaining, the pine cabinets hold your cookware and appliances plus a dishwasher is available for your convenience. Enjoy direct access to the beautiful back deck from here, boasting wonderful outdoor patio furnishings, propane BBQ, and a pellet smoker for your use, you will love spending your evenings unwinding here while grilling up dinner or sipping your first cup of coffee among the birds in the morning.&lt;br /&gt;
