property.description:
Mountain Getaway Big Bear - Cozy Family Retreat&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Mountain Getaway lives up to its name as the perfect relaxation destination for a group of friends, couple&amp;#39;s getaway, or small family vacation to the mountains. Sitting on a quiet tree lined property in Sugarloaf you will be within a quick ten-minute car ride to the ski resorts, lake, or Village shops for entertainment. Fully furnished with all that you need for a memorable and relaxing vacation this single level cozy chalet is a guest favorite home away from home to return to year after year.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Snuggle up on the plush couches together as you warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace and watch the snow falling through the big open windows. A flat screen Streaming TV and complimentary hi speed WIFI internet are provided for your enjoyment so you can pop on your favorite movie or show. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) The open floor plan flows seamlessly to the adorable dining table and breakfast bar where you can enjoy comfortable seating together for your meals between the bistro table and added bar stools. The chef of your group will love this adorable yet well equipped kitchen here at Mountain Getaway- you will have all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals right here at the cabin. Freshly painted oak cabinets are stocked full with cookware and utensils for your use along with general appliances and even a stacked washer and dryer for your added convenience to handle those wet snow clothes or extended visits to Big Bear.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Being a single level chalet you will have quick and convenient access to both of your cozy bedrooms and the hallway bathroom, all of which are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your group when you arrive for your vacation. Both rooms offer their own Streaming TV for your added enjoyment plus there is quick backyard access from the convenient side door off of the kitchen area.&amp;nbsp;Outside you will find yourselves surrounded by pine trees and other cute cabins here in this quiet residential neighborhood, a fully fenced yard and adorable entry sun deck offer a great space to sip your first cup of coffee in the mornings with the birds. If you aren&amp;#39;t wanting to make the ten minute drive into town you can also stroll down to the nearby Sugarloaf market or Kallan&amp;#39;s diner right here in your neighborhood as well as a kids play and skate park and access to local Maple Hill Trails for the hiking and biking enthusiasts in your group. Mountain Getaway truly is the perfect destination for any season, you will love your visit here!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
