&lt;br /&gt;
Soaring Pines truly is a one-of-a-kind custom-built mountain chalet offering all that you need for the ultimate vacation to the mountains. Sitting atop a half acre of private Fox Farm property yet within minutes to the lake, skiing, or shopping this is the ultimate vacation destination featuring a custom stone driveway and basketball court, ample outdoor entertainment areas, a Barbeque grill, outdoor seating, and beautiful touches throughout including an English pergola garden with a fountain, seasonal fruit trees on site, and custom made ski lift chairs to relax and unwind as you enjoy your time in the mountains.&lt;br /&gt;
