property.description:
Apres Ski Haus | Hot Tub | Pool Table | Arcade| Central&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for families, friends, or a corporate retreat, Apres Ski Haus offers the ultimate Big Bear getaway year-round. Located in the sought-after Evergreen Estates/Heavenly Valley neighborhood, this spacious two-story chalet is just minutes from Snow Summit ski/bike park, the lake, marina, grocery stores, and the Village.&lt;br /&gt;
Step into the stunning great room with soaring knotty pine ceilings, large picture windows, and hardwood floors. Relax by the wood-burning stove on cozy couches or stream your favorite shows using the complimentary high-speed Wi-Fi (guests provide their own streaming accounts). A separate family room offers a second wood stove, a library, a streaming TV, a pool table, and a sit-down arcade game&amp;mdash;ensuring endless entertainment for everyone.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The open floor plan connects the living area to a fully equipped kitchen and dining space. Chefs will love the gourmet kitchen featuring stainless appliances, double burners, dual ovens, and a dishwasher. Enjoy meals together at dual dining tables or the breakfast bar. The main-level primary suite boasts a private bath with a claw-foot tub and steam shower. Additional bedrooms and bathrooms are upstairs, each thoughtfully prepared with fresh linens and towels. A laundry room and half bath on the lower level add convenience.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Outside, unwind on the large wraparound deck with patio furnishings, surrounded by seasonal landscaping and mountain greenery. After a day of adventure, soak in the hot tub under the stars. With its modern amenities, cozy mountain charm, and unbeatable location, Apres Ski Haus is your perfect escape to Big Bear. Book your stay today!&lt;br /&gt;
