property.description:
Wolf Creek Castle at Big Bear Resort&amp;nbsp;| Spa&amp;nbsp;| Slopes&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Experience the epitome of mountain luxury at Wolf Creek Castle, where your Big Bear vacation reaches new heights. Nestled in a private gated community, this exceptional mountain retreat offers breathtaking views of Bear Mountain&amp;#39;s golf course or ski slopes. Renowned for its entertainment prowess, Wolf Creek Castle introduces a new level of relaxation with a spa on the upper-level deck and a surround sound TV in the loft. Indulge in the spacious and inviting living room adorned with unique tree and pine accents, solid hickory floors, and expansive windows framing the panoramic views. Gather around the floor-to-ceiling rock wood-burning fireplace, creating a cozy haven for cherished moments with loved ones. Enjoy movie nights on the mounted flat-screen streaming TV, or utilize the convenient work desk for a perfect stay-cation&lt;br /&gt;
.&lt;br /&gt;
The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living area to the expansive kitchen and dining spaces, fostering an ideal environment for entertaining. The chef in your group will appreciate the well-equipped kitchen, featuring beautiful oak cabinets, high-end appliances, and a built-in beverage cooler. The custom log table furnishings in the formal dining room complement the breakfast bar, ensuring ample seating for your group. Discover the delights of the game room loft upstairs, where entertainment reigns supreme. Engage in friendly competition with pool or Foosball, or unwind by the wood-burning fireplace and streaming TV. Access the upper-level sun deck, where a private hot tub awaits, offering a perfect retreat under the stars.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
For added convenience, a separate storage room accommodates snow gear or lake toys, while a laundry room with a washer and dryer is on hand for your convenience. With heated bathroom floors and double tankless water heaters, Wolf Creek Castle is designed for the utmost comfort during your mountain escape. This chalet caters to large groups, ensuring that all rooms are meticulously prepared with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels upon your arrival. Grill up a delicious dinner on the provided propane BBQ or unwind in the hot tub, soaking in the serenity of the surroundings. From top to bottom, Wolf Creek Castle is meticulously furnished with your vacation experience in mind, offering true rustic mountain elegance. Spoil yourselves with an unforgettable retreat in the lap of luxury at Wolf Creek Castle!&lt;br /&gt;
