property.description:
Brownie&amp;#39;s Den | Walk to Slopes Townhouse&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Brownie&amp;#39;s Den is the perfect escape destination for a group of friends or small family to fully enjoy the best of Big Bear- freshly renovated with your vacation stay in mind and located right below Snow Summit Ski Resort you will have quick and easy access to local fun. Boasting light and bright modern interior furnishings along with the essentials from home create a memorable and relaxing vacation in the mountains no matter the season you choose to visit.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter your chalet on the second middle level where you are greeted with gorgeous hardwood floors and cozy furnishings- you will immediately feel like you are in the mountains here. Snuggle up on the cozy couch as you warm your toes in front of the brick gas fireplace and watch a movie on the mounted flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi-speed WIFI internet is provided for your convenience throughout the property. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming services.) The open floor plan leads seamlessly to the cute dining area and equipped kitchen where the chef of your group will find all that you need to whip up your home-cooked meals right here at the condo. The breakfast bar stools pair perfectly with the bistro-style dining table to ensure your whole group can sit comfortably together and enjoy your meals. You will love the fresh and modern kitchen stocked full of cookware and utensils along with stainless appliances and a dishwasher to ensure your cleanup is a breeze.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The spacious primary suite offers a beautiful accent wall, Streaming TV, and access out to the great sun deck while the guest bedroom offers a convenient bunk bed set for the group- all of your rooms are made up for your group&amp;#39;s arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your trip. Two full bathrooms and a separate laundry room are on hand offering you a washer and dryer for those wet snow clothes or extended visits to the mountains. Enjoy the beautiful mountain evenings on the patio with your favorite beverage. You are a short walk to the lifts at Snow Summit Resort or a quick car ride to the grocery store, marina, or even the Village shops making this an unbeatable central spot to enjoy your trip.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
