Welcome to Elmwood Place!! This is the perfect destination for a group of friends or a family looking to make the most of their time in the mountains at Big Bear. Freshly furnished with mountain charm and the necessities from home our cozy two level retreat sits on a spacious tree lined and fully fenced private property in a quiet and relaxing neighborhood on the East side of town. Hop in the car and your group is within a short ten minute drive to all local activities including the ski resorts, marina, and even the downtown Village shops for dining and entertainment.&lt;br /&gt;
