property.description:
Bear Mountain Views |&amp;nbsp;Relaxing Resort Retreat&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Bear Mountain Views! This charming multi-level, 3-bedroom cabin offers an exceptional retreat nestled in the heart of Big Bear Lake, across from the renowned Bear Mountain Ski Resort or a short ride on the free shuttle to Snow Summit Ski Resort. Perfectly positioned to take full advantage of the stunning mountain vistas, this home boasts gorgeous panoramic views of Bear Mountain, making it the ideal escape for outdoor enthusiasts and those looking to unwind in nature&amp;#39;s beauty. The second level deck provides a place for families and friends&amp;nbsp;to gather and enjoy a BBQ while taking in the amazing scenery.&lt;br /&gt;
.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The cabin features a spacious and open living area with large windows that invite natural light and showcase breathtaking views of the surrounding mountains. The cozy living room, complete with a stone fireplace, offers a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for relaxing after a day of skiing or hiking.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
The fully equipped kitchen and dining area provide plenty of space for family meals or gathering with friends, while the cabin&amp;#39;s multiple levels offer ample privacy and flexibility. Each of the three bedrooms is tastefully and comfortably furnished. The third level loft offers spectacular views of Bear Mountain as well as foosball and a place to relax and play games.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Located within walking distance to Bear Mountain Resort, you&amp;rsquo;ll have easy access to world-class skiing, snowboarding, and hiking trails. For golf enthusiasts, the Bear Mountain Golf Course is right across the street, and the Big Bear Alpine Zoo is a short drive, providing a unique and educational experience for all ages.&lt;br /&gt;
With its perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm, this cabin offers a peaceful yet convenient location to explore the best of Big Bear. Whether you&amp;#39;re hitting the slopes, enjoying a round of golf, or simply soaking in the serene mountain atmosphere, this home provides the perfect base for your Big Bear adventures.&lt;br /&gt;
