&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for a couple&amp;#39;s getaway, group of friends, or larger family vacation to the mountains our Flitterbick Lodge is the perfect place to spend your time together creating a memorable and relaxing vacation to Big Bear. Located in Fawnskin you are just ten minutes by car to the local activities in Big Bear yet secluded in a quiet neighborhood on the North Shore of the lake.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
