&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Emma&amp;#39;s Cottage. A spacious two-story retreat cottage nestled in the pines and providing the perfect setting for a group of friends or family vacation to the mountains. Located in a quiet Sugarloaf neighborhood on the east side of town you are within a short walk to local hiking trails and a quick ten-minute car ride to town for activities.&lt;br /&gt;
