Boasting all that you need for a memorable vacation in the mountains our adorable chalet is packed with entertainment and convenience right at your fingertips. Whip up your home cooked meals in the equipped kitchen and dining area complete with stainless appliances and cookware with a convenient modern hallway bathroom and laundry area quickly accessible from here. Snuggle up and watch the snow falling as you warm your toes by the fire and pop on a movie on the flatscreen Streaming TV in the cozy living room. Upstairs a private bedroom and oversized landing area provides plenty of comfortable space when you are ready for a great night of rest plus offers a PlayStation gaming system and dartboard to keep you entertained.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step outside where you are emersed in nature as you have a fully fenced and private backyard at your fingertips including life sized games like Jenga, Connect Four, and Cornhole- you&amp;#39;ll be playing out here together all day. On the front side of the cabin, you can enjoy a spacious sun deck complete with patio furnishings, a fun firepit where you can unwind by the fire, and a propane BBQ so you can grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake. Emma&amp;#39;s Cottage has it all- come experience your new home away from home in the mountains today!&lt;br /&gt;
