&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Smith Chalet at Snow Summit- this is the perfect base camp retreat for a group of friends or family vacation to Big Bear- located just below Snow Summit Resort this almost ski-in chalet is freshly furnished and renovated with your vacation stay in mind and provides all that you need for a relaxing vacation no matter the season you choose to visit. Walk just a few feet from your door and you are at the lifts for wintertime skiing and summertime bike park activities or hop in the car and you are within a short ten minute drive to local activities including the marina, village shops, and grocery stores- you can&amp;#39;t beat this incredible location for your next trip to Big Bear!&lt;br /&gt;
