property.description:
Green Canoe Cabin&amp;nbsp;| Central Retreat w/&amp;nbsp;Hot Tub&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for a group of friends or family looking to getaway to the mountains to relax in comfort and style under soaring pine trees our Green Canoe Cabin has been meticulously renovated and furnished with your vacation stay in mind to provide your group with a comfortable and cozy vacation home to make lifelong memories together no matter the season you choose to visit Big Bear. Centrally located in lower Moonridge your group will be within a short car ride to local activities including the ski resorts, golf, zoo, and hiking trails right outside your doorstep- the possibilities are endless from this base camp chalet cabin.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter the lower entry level where you are greeted with gorgeous hardwood floors and big open windows that provide the perfect balance of natural lighting and forested views of the snow falling outside in the winter months. Enjoy snuggling up together on the cozy couch as you warm your toes in front of the toasty gas faux log fireplace as you pop on a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI internet supplied for your enjoyment. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) The open floor plan flows seamlessly to the kitchen and dining areas which is perfect for entertaining a group or hosting your next family holiday in the mountains. The chef of your group will have immediate access to all that you need for preparing your home cooked meals here in the adorable galley style kitchen- complete with fresh cabinets stocked full with cookware and utensils, general appliances including a dishwasher, and a formal log dining table where you can enjoy your time together as a group.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The lower level guest room and bathroom offer quick and convenient access to cozy sleeping spaces for part of your group along with a washer and dryer for those wet snow clothes or extended visits to the mountains any time of the year. Venturing upstairs you will find another guest room and the spacious primary suite which offers vaulted ceilings, a private fireplace, balcony, and bathroom for your added convenience. All of your rooms and bathrooms are made up for your group with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your vacation stay when you arrive. Venture outside to truly relax and unwind under soaring pine trees as you enjoy the pet friendly and fully fenced spacious property complete with a wonderful patio area featuring a gas BBQ to grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake and your own private hot tub- you will love soaking your muscles here after a fun day of adventures out on the lake or mountain. Green Canoe Cabin is an exceptional choice for your next vacation- come experience your newest home away from home in the mountains today!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Queen Bed- Downstairs Entry Level&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: King Bed, Gas Fireplace, Streaming TV, Private Balcony- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3: Twin/Full Bunk - Upstairs 2nd Level&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Private 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)- Bedroom 2- Upstairs 2nd Level&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
-Sleeps 6&lt;br /&gt;
-3 Cars Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
-1 Pet Welcome w/ Additional Fee&lt;br /&gt;
-1,286 Total Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
