&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Storyville | Hot Tub &amp;middot; Arcade &amp;middot; Walk To Marina Cabin&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Storyville is the perfect destination for a couple&amp;#39;s getaway, small group of friends, or even a cozy family vacation to the mountains. This adorable cabin is small and intimate and comfortably sleeps up to 3 guests. Come indulge in style and comfort as you relax under soaring pine trees and shooting stars just blocks from the lake and the downtown Village. Freshly renovated from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind, our adorable single-level chalet is packed with all that you need to enjoy the very best of Big Bear no matter the season you choose to visit.&lt;br /&gt;
Enter your chalet where you are met with gorgeous hardwood floors, knotty pine cathedral ceilings, and big open windows that provide the perfect balance of natural lighting and views of the forested neighborhood outside. You can snuggle up together on the oversized sectional as you warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace and pop on your favorite movie on the mounted flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary high speed WIFI internet supplied for your enjoyment. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) The open floor plan flows seamlessly to the breakfast bar and dining area where you&amp;#39;ll find plenty of comfortable space to enjoy your meals as a group. The cute and modern chef&amp;#39;s kitchen has all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals and holiday feasts including freshly painted cabinets stocked with cookware and utensils, new countertops and prep space, plus stainless steel appliances. Enjoy a game of vintage Asteroids on the stand up game machine here in the open space between the living and dining areas you are sure to be entertained for hours trying to beat the high score.&lt;br /&gt;
Down the hall you will find two spacious bedrooms and a freshly remodeled hallway bathroom, each offers open windows and dresser space for your packed belongings and is made up for your group&amp;#39;s arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your stay. Venture out back to enjoy a private and fully fenced backyard which offers a propane BBQ to grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake along with your own private hot tub where you can soak those muscles after a fun day of adventures on the lake or mountain. Boasting great year-round flat parking, easy level entry, and a wonderful central location, you can stroll to the lake or Village shops on foot or hop in the car and be within five minutes to grocery stores, marinas, and the local ski resorts. Storyville has it all, come experience this adorable home away from home in the mountains for your next vacation today!&lt;br /&gt;
