&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Pine Nest! Sitting right by Holloways Marina and within a short stroll to the downtown Village this mountain retreat is the perfect destination for any group to spend their next vacation to Big Bear! Sip your morning coffee with the birds or enjoy incredible sunset views from the great patio deck or snuggle up in front of the toasty fireplace as you enjoy the mountains together, the possibilities are endless from here! Hop in the car and you are just ten minutes to local ski resorts, grocery stores, and activities.&lt;br /&gt;
