&lt;br /&gt;
Experience the ultimate mountain getaway at this exquisite home, situated in the serene wilderness just outside of Big Bear Village. This newly built 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath residence perfectly embodies the essence of contemporary mountain living, seamlessly blending rustic charm with modern sophistication. It provides a peaceful retreat from the everyday hustle and bustle. Nestled in a tranquil and secluded setting, this home allows you to fully immerse yourself in the natural splendor of the Big Bear Lake region. While the lively Big Bear Village, offering its array of shops, restaurants, and entertainment options, is just a short drive away, you&amp;#39;ll find solace and serenity at this mountain oasis.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
From the ground up, this home is entirely brand new, incorporating the latest amenities and eco-friendly features to ensure both comfort and sustainability. Boasting four bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, it offers ample space for your family and guests. The layout is thoughtfully designed, creating open areas for socializing and cozy nooks for relaxation. The chef&amp;#39;s kitchen features top-tier stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a convenient island for casual dining, making it the perfect space for preparing meals and hosting gatherings. The master bedroom is a true sanctuary, complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom featuring a soaking tub and a walk-in closet. A private balcony reveals breathtaking views of the surrounding forest, while the deck offers an ideal spot for al fresco dining, stargazing, or simply enjoying your morning coffee amidst the tranquil mountain panoramas.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
