property.description:
Maltby Modern Log Cabin&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;Relaxing Bear City Retreat with Outdoor SPA&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for your next family vacation or getaway to the mountains with friends our Maltby Modern Log Cabin is exactly what you need to enjoy a relaxing and comfortable vacation under soaring pine trees and shooting stars. Freshly renovated with your getaway experience in mind you&amp;#39;ll have all that you need on hand to enjoy the very best of Big Bear no matter the season you choose to visit. Hop in the car and you are just ten minutes from the lake, grocery stores, and the local ski resorts- the possibilities are truly endless from the escape cabin!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter your cozy living room where you are greeted with fresh carpet and paint, soaring ceilings, and big open windows that provide you with the perfect balance of natural lighting and forested views of the quiet neighborhood outside. Snuggle up together here on the comfy couch as you warm your toes in front of the colossal stone wood burning fireplace which reaches from the floor to the ceiling and pairs with a mounted flat screen Streaming TV so you can lounge and enjoy a movie night at the cabin. Around the corner your modern chef&amp;#39;s kitchen offers all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals and holiday feasts at the cabin including freshly painted and fully stocked oak cabinets, stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher and a separate washer and dryer for those wet snow clothes and extended visits to the mountains&lt;br /&gt;
