&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Jay Bird Landing Escape- our furnished and spacious two story retreat offers the perfect destination for a group of friends or family to getaway together to make lifelong memories under soaring pine trees any time of the year. This private fenced property sits right along the Big Bear Airport and is within a quick stroll to the Oktoberfest or a short ten minute car ride to local ski resorts and lake activities. Enjoy soaking your muscles in the private hot tub after a fun day of adventure out on the lake or mountain- this packed chalet truly has it all!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
