property.description:
Lakefront Village Castle&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;Amazing Lake Views&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Brace yourselves for the vacation of a lifetime here at Lakefront Village Castle! Completely renovated from head to toe with your vacation experience in mind and perfect for a group getaway to the lake or family vacation to the mountains our spacious castle offers all that you need to vacation in comfort and style together right on the shore of Big Bear Lake in the heart of the downtown Village. Gourmet kitchen and dining essentials pair with added entertainment and modern mountain amenities within this amazing lakefront bay location which includes your own private boat dock for the lake toys in the warmer months- come experience this incredible vacation home away from home for your next retreat today!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter the lower level of your mountain chalet where you are greeted with big open windows that provide the perfect balance of natural lighting and amazing views of the lake and marina outside. The chef of your group will find all that you need to prepare your home cooked meals and family holiday feasts packed into the gourmet kitchen and formal dining area, complete with oak cabinets stocked with cookware and utensils, general appliances, and a dishwasher to ensure your cleanup is a breeze here. Cozy up together in the den which offers the lower level bathroom and a separate laundry room with a washer and dryer for those wet snow clothes or extended visits to the mountains any time of the year. Challenge the group at a game of foosball or pop on your favorite movie on many flat screen Streaming TVs throughout the property. Warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace as you watch the snow falling outside in the winter months or head out on the lake for fishing and boating activities right from your cabin.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Head upstairs where your three spacious sleeping quarters and two of the group&amp;#39;s bathrooms are located, each room offers a mounted flat screen Streaming TV, warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels as well as incredible lake and valley views. The spacious primary suite offers incredible views and a private attached bathroom for the group&amp;#39;s added privacy. Outside the perfectly manicured property offers plenty of relaxing spaces for you to spend your time unwinding under soaring pine trees and shooting stars and includes a great patio area and sun decks with a propane BBQ for you to grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake. The seasonal boat dock gives you the opportunity to rent lake toys and make the most out of this amazing location. Packed with all that you need to make lifelong memories together at Big Bear your group will want to return year after year to your new home away from home on the lake!&lt;br /&gt;
