The Eagles Nest | Hot Tub | BBQ | Modern Retreat&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for a couple&amp;#39;s vacation or small family retreat to the mountains head on up to enjoy endless hours of fresh air and relaxation here at The Eagles Nest where you can appreciate our adorable modernized cottage in the woods. Featuring light and bright concepts throughout your spacious two story property which sits on a tree lined double lot with plenty of year round parking available. Packed from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind you will have all that you need to create lifelong memories here in the mountains together and includes your own private hot tub under the stars out back where you will be sure to soak away your fun day of adventures on the lake.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter your lower level where you are greeted with a spacious open interior showcasing wood planked beamed ceilings, new flooring, dual pane windows and an updated kitchen that&amp;#39;s both efficient &amp;amp; beautiful! Snuggle up together and warm your toes in front of the toasty gas faux log fireplace as you pop on a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV and watch the snow falling outside. Complimentary hi speed WIFI internet is supplied for your enjoyment however guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services. Prepare and enjoy your home cooked meals and holiday feasts right here at the cabin with plenty of dining space paired with cookware and utensils for your use in the oak cabinets.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
A beautiful hallway full bath is easily accessible here on the lower entry level while the living room sofa doubles as added sleeping space when you are ready for a great night of rest. Upstairs is a classic cottage open loft bedroom (no door) featuring ample space with vaulted A-frame wood beamed ceilings that create the perfect mountain ambiance for bed, all of your rooms are made up for your arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels when you arrive for your vacation stay. Step outside to enjoy the tree lined mountain property complete with patio sun decks and a private hot tub of your own where you can relax and unwind in the evenings as you soak your muscles after a fun day out on the mountain or grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake on the propane BBQ. Close to amazing restaurants, shops, hiking &amp;amp; the local ski resort, this home is a perfect balance of nature &amp;amp; world famous Big Bear amenities, come experience your new home away from home in the mountains today!&lt;br /&gt;
