property.description:
Silvertip Pines | Cozy Hillside Log Cabin Retreat&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Silvertip Pines! Your group will absolutely love your vacation stay here at our relaxing and modern hillside retreat, freshly furnished from head to toe with your experience in mind and packed with all that you need to relax and unwind under soaring pine trees and millions of stars anytime of the year. Centrally located in a quiet forested neighborhood you have the best of Big Bear within a short ten minute drive from your cabin including local marinas, village shops, and ski resorts.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter the cozy lower level where you are greeted with hardwood floors, wood beamed ceilings, and big open windows that provide the perfect balance of natural lighting and forested views of the treetops below. You will love snuggling up here on the couch together as you warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace and pop on your favorite movie on the flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI internet supplied for your convenience. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) The cute guest bedroom and bathroom are easily accessible here on the entry level along with a washer and dryer for those wet snow clothes or extended visits to the mountains.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Head upstairs to find two additional sleeping quarters and an added bathroom for your party, each room is made up for your arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your vacation stay. Venture out to the great outdoors to enjoy relaxing sun decks and a propane firepit and BBQ where you can warm up on a chilly evening as you grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake under soaring pine trees. Soak your muscles under the stars in your own private hot tub out back after an adventurous day out on the mountain. This relaxing retreat truly has it all. Silvertip Pines is an amazing retreat, perfect for any group no matter the season you choose to visit Big Bear- come experience your newest home away from home together today!&lt;br /&gt;
