property.description:
The Pines Retreat&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;Impeccable Modern Village Cabin&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Nestled under soaring pine trees and shooting stars just outside of the charming Big Bear Village your group will fall in love with the San Bernardino Mountains here at The Pines Retreat, this magnificent residence is the epitome of modern luxury and comfortable living and includes meticulous attention to detail and elegant design throughout offering the ideal blend of aesthetics, convenience, and functionality for your next vacation. The attached two car garage and easy flat parking is convenient for any group no matter the season you choose to visit.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Boasting a reverse floor plan you will step inside your stunning property on the upstairs level where you&amp;#39;ll be immediately impressed by the open light-filled floor plan complete with gorgeous hardwood floors and high quality finishes that grace every room of your home.&amp;nbsp;The spacious living room features soaring ceilings full of large windows that invite natural light and snow filled views, and a cozy fireplace that creates the perfect ambiance for relaxation and entertaining.&amp;nbsp;The gourmet kitchen is a culinary enthusiast&amp;#39;s dream, equipped with state-of-the-art appliances, granite countertops, a large island for prep and casual dining, and ample cabinet space. It seamlessly flows into the formal dining area, making it an ideal space for family gatherings or hosting dinner parties.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The separate laundry room and hallway powder room offer convenience and essentials no matter the season you visit while the lower level game room is packed with all the entertainment a group would need for a family vacation or getaway with friends in the mountains. Play a game on the ping-pong table, foosball, or arcade game or just lounge on the futon couches and enjoy a movie on the Streaming TV- this home truly has it all. Four spacious bedrooms offer tranquility and privacy for your group making it easy to unwind and relax after a long day. Step outside to enjoy spacious sun decks among the tree tops and a open forested backyard which provides the perfect spot for outdoor dining, barbecues, or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings.&amp;nbsp;This remarkable home is ideally situated close to the vibrant village, offering convenient access to shopping, dining, cultural events, and community amenities. Come experience your next vacation here at The Pines Retreat!&lt;br /&gt;
