&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Tomeny Cabin! Nestled in a tranquil wooded setting, this charming retreat blends rustic allure with modern comforts and essentials to provide the perfect setting for a large family vacation or group getaway to the mountains. Located in a quiet central neighborhood you will have quick and convenient access to local activities and events including the ski resorts, zoo, grocery stores, and Village shops.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Boasting two spacious levels of sprawling space for you to enjoy this equipped cabin offers an open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining and staying connected with your group. Snuggle up on the couch and warm your toes in front of the fireplace as you pop on a movie on the mounted Streaming TV or whip up something delicious in the equipped chef&amp;#39;s kitchen complete with stainless appliances and cookware.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Four spacious sleeping areas offer the perfect blend of modern amenities and comforts from home when you are ready for a great night of rest. Two modern bathrooms are easily accessible and made up for your arrival plus a stacked laundry facility is available for those wet snow clothes. You&amp;#39;ll love layout of this house with two bedrooms on each level, the upstairs bunk room has a fun foosball table for hours of entertainment while the primary suite offers a private balcony deck for a more intimate experience with nature.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Venture outside where you are immersed in nature among the treetops from the elevated sun deck, complete with patio furnishings, a propane BBQ, and relaxing forested views. The open property is perfect for safe snow play and sledding right from the side of the cabin within this quiet yet central neighborhood. Hop in the car and you are under ten minutes to local activities- this chalet has it all. Come experience your new home away from home at Big Bear today here at Tomeny Cabin!&lt;br /&gt;
