property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Vista Pines at Big Bear Lake&amp;ndash; Your Ultimate Mountain Escape&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Vista Pines, where timeless vintage charm meets exceptional modern luxury! This newly remodeled 1940s single-story cabin is the epitome of elegance and comfort, offering a one-of-a-kind mountain retreat. Every inch of this home has been thoughtfully designed with luxurious finishes and features that will leave you feeling pampered and relaxed from the moment you arrive.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step inside and be amazed by the all-new appliances, including a gourmet kitchen with sleek, state-of-the-art finishes, perfect for preparing your favorite meals. The open-concept floor plan creates a seamless flow from room to room, making it easy to unwind or entertain. With brand-new furniture throughout, including plush, stylish seating and eye-catching d&amp;eacute;cor, Vista Pines combines the best of rustic charm with modern sophistication. Power window coverings, a brand-new AC unit, and dual washer/dryer units provide the ultimate convenience and comfort for your stay, no matter the season. From the toasty wood-burning fireplace to the luxurious linens in the bedrooms and the thoughtfully designed layout, every detail at Vista Pines is tailored for a memorable and rejuvenating experience.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The spacious and private backyard is a true highlight, offering plenty of room for snowball fights or snow angels in the winter, and transforming into the perfect spot for starlit dinners or relaxing evenings under the crisp mountain air during the summer months. After a day of adventure, head out to the sun deck, equipped with comfortable outdoor furnishings and a Propane BBQ, and enjoy a delicious meal while soaking in the natural beauty of the area. Vista Pines is located just a 5-minute walk to Big Bear Lake, so you&amp;rsquo;re never far from the water&amp;rsquo;s edge, and a short drive from the charming Village, local hiking trails, grocery stores, and the famous Big Bear Ski Resorts. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re seeking an active getaway filled with outdoor exploration or a peaceful retreat to unwind, Vista Pines offers the perfect balance of excitement and tranquility.&lt;br /&gt;
