Crescenta Pines Resort Log Cabin&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;Hot Tub | Games&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Crescentia Pines Log Cabin- this is the quintessential log cabin in the woods and is perfect retreat for a group getaway or family vacation to the mountains any time of the year. Relax and unwind together under soaring pine trees and shooting stars as you enjoy the best of Big Bear right at your fingertips paired with the finest amenities and essentials right here at your cabin. The owners have recently renovated with your vacation experience in mind and have left nothing out. Come see this extraordinary mountain gem for yourselves!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sitting atop a hill in a quiet upper Moonridge neighborhood your heavily forested property provides your group with plenty of privacy and space to safely play and indulge in the nature around you. Enter through the grand entrance where you&amp;#39;ll be greeted with knotty pine vaulted cathedral ceilings, gorgeous hardwood floors and big open windows which provide the perfect amount of natural lighting within a spacious open floor plan- you can truly feel right at home here at this chalet. Snuggle up together and warm your toes in front of the toasty fireplace as you watch the snow falling from the big open windows and pop on a movie on the mounted flat screen Streaming TV. Your chef will adore the equipped kitchen and dining area here at Crescentia Pines, perfect for entertaining and preparing your home cooked holiday meals and slope side snacks any time of the year you will find all that you need right here. Beautiful pine cabinets are stocked with cookware and utensils while new granite counters, general appliances and a dishwasher ensures that your cleanup is a breeze.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Being a spacious single level chalet your group has quick and convenient access to your three sleeping quarters and both bathrooms as well as a stacked washer and dryer in the hallway which is perfect for those wet snow clothes or extended stays in the mountains. Each room offers big open windows, comfortable beds, warm linens, and fresh bath towels for your group when you arrive and is setup perfectly to ensure your group can enjoy a great night of restful sleep. If the kids get bored you can send them out to the attached garage where they can enjoy the foosball and arcade game. Venture out back where you are sure to spend most of your time here in the mountains on the spacious sun deck with a propane BBQ and your own private hot tub under the stars- you will love soaking your muscles here under the stars after a fun day out on the mountain. Within minutes of tons of local hiking trails and a short ten minute drive to either ski resorts, marinas, and Village shops this location truly can&amp;#39;t be beat. Grab the gang and head up to Big Bear to experience the vacation of a lifetime here at your new home away from home!&lt;br /&gt;
