Gold Rush Lodge Big Bear | Hot Tub&amp;nbsp;| Games&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Gold Rush Lodge, an enchanting retreat where the allure of rustic elegance harmonizes effortlessly with contemporary comfort. Nestled in the heart of the mountains, this extraordinary 6-bedroom haven is meticulously designed to deliver an unforgettable experience for those in search of the perfect fusion of relaxation and entertainment. Approach the residence via a unique driveway doubling as a picturesque bridge, guiding you to the grand entrance of our opulent log cabin. The exterior proudly displays the timeless craftsmanship of a classic log cabin, while the interior beckons you into a realm of luxury and amusement.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Featuring six meticulously appointed bedrooms, there is abundant space for everyone in your party. Each room seamlessly blends comfort and style, promising a tranquil night&amp;#39;s sleep amidst the mountain&amp;#39;s breathtaking beauty. The whimsical bunk room, offering direct access to the outdoor spa, invites both the young and the young at heart to unwind. Complete with a ping pong table, it ensures continuous entertainment for all ages. The focal point of Gold Rush Lodge is its welcoming living room, anchored by a majestic fireplace radiating warmth and charm. Immerse yourself in your favorite shows and movies on the surround sound TV, or simply bask in the glow of the crackling fire. The cabin&amp;#39;s game room is a true delight, boasting a handsomely adorned bear-themed bar, a pool table, and a dartboard, providing limitless options for enjoyment and relaxation.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
For the culinary enthusiasts, the well-appointed kitchen is a chef&amp;#39;s haven, equipped with modern appliances and everything necessary to craft gourmet meals. Whether you&amp;#39;re whipping up culinary masterpieces or brewing a cup of coffee, the exquisite log dining table sets the perfect stage.&amp;nbsp; Step outside and embrace the natural beauty that envelops Gold Rush Lodge. Whether you&amp;#39;re indulging in the spa, challenging companions to a ping pong match, or simply lounging on the deck, the serene mountain environment seamlessly becomes an integral part of your experience. Our luxury log cabin guarantees an unforgettable mountain escape, skillfully blending the charm of a traditional log cabin with modern amenities. Whether you&amp;#39;re celebrating with family and friends or seeking a tranquil getaway, Gold Rush Lodge offers an unparalleled experience. Secure your stay today and embark on a journey to create cherished memories in this mountain paradise.&lt;br /&gt;
