&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Skyline Lodge! Your home away from home awaits you here in this beautiful single level newly constructed mountain log cabin chalet. Relax under soaring pine trees and shooting stars anytime of the year from our furnished upper Moonridge retreat. Hop in the car and you are within a short ten minute car ride to local ski resorts, golf, and the Alpine Zoo, this is an unbeatable year round central location for any season. Elevate your next getaway with friends or family vacation to new heights here at Skyline Lodge!&lt;br /&gt;
