&amp;nbsp;
&lt;div&gt;Welcome to Bear Paw Cottage! Our 2-bedroom retreat is your ideal home away from home in the mountains&amp;nbsp;offering a perfect blend of relaxation, adventure, and creature comforts. It&amp;#39;s the ideal retreat for nature lovers, outdoor enthusiasts, and anyone looking to escape to the beauty of Big Bear while enjoying the company of their four-legged friends. This adorable log cabin is where you want to spend your time from that city life. Spend your evening in the mountains soaking in the backyard&amp;#39;s private hot tub, barbecuing or relaxing and sipping your first cup of coffee in the morning listening to the birds chirping and looking at the beautiful pines.&lt;/div&gt;
