Timber Pines Chalet&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;Hot Tub&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;Walk to Lake/Marina&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Timber Pines Chalet! Relax and enjoy the serenity of Big Bear here within a bright and airy quintessential single level retreat nestled in the heart of Boulder Bay. The spacious treed and fenced property offers privacy and seclusion while still within ten minutes to local activities and a short walk to the lake or marina. Freshly renovated from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind our tree house chalet offers all that you need for a memorable and relaxing visit to the mountains and is topped off by your own private hot tub under the stars.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Revel in the ambiance created by the wood beamed vaulted ceilings pairing with beautiful hardwood floors and modern comforts throughout, you will truly feel right at home at this tree house from the moment you enter. Snuggle up together on the couch and watch the snow falling from the massive picture windows or pop on a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV for a movie night at the cabin. The open space floor plan leads seamlessly to the dining area with a decorative vintage wood stove and the equipped chef&amp;#39;s kitchen complete with all that you need to prepare home cooked meals here at the cabin including freshly painted cabinets, cookware, utensils, general appliances, and a dishwasher to ensure a breezy cleanup afterwards.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Being a single level retreat you will have quick and convenient access to both of your sleeping quarters and modern bathrooms, each offers open windows, new beds, and will be made up for your arrival with warm linens, blankets, and fresh bath towels for your vacation stay. A separate laundry room area offers a great space for storing lake toys or ski gear and offers a washer and dryer for those wet snow clothes or extended visits to the mountain any time of the year and is also your access point to the back deck and yard where you will be sure to spend your evenings relaxing under soaring pine trees as you soak your muscles in your private hot tub as you look for shooting stars. Timber Pines Chalet has it all- oozing charm and seamlessly blending indoor and outdoor living in the mountains all while sitting in an unbeatable central location. Come see your new home away from home at Big Bear today!&lt;br /&gt;
