&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to The Rustic Retreat! Your group will fall in love with this charming&amp;nbsp; and airy two story cabin located in a highly desirable neighborhood in Big Bear Lake. Ordained in big open windows and an abundance of natural lighting this homey yet spacious chalet offers a serene retreat for families, friends and our 4 legged loved ones including a fully fenced private yard. Boasting all that you need to experience a relaxing vacation under the stars you will love your vacation here at The Rustic Retreat!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter the lower level where you will find two spacious sleeping quarters and the main guest bathroom. Head upstairs to the main level where you are greeted with vaulted wood beamed ceilings within a warm and cozy living space, perfect for relaxing after a fun day of adventures out on the mountain or lake. Snuggle up together and warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace as you watch the snow falling outside. The open floorplan is perfect for entertaining groups as it flows seamlessly into the equipped kitchen and open dining area.&amp;nbsp; Here you will find all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals and slope side snacks for the group plus a cute dining table offers a great space for you to enjoy your meals together and enjoy the forested views.&lt;br /&gt;
