property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Restmoore Big Bear | Boulder Bay Condo | Pool, Spa, Ski Shuttle, Remote Office&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Restmoore, a bold and beautifully appointed mountain retreat in the prime Boulder Bay neighborhood of Big Bear Lake, California. Designed for effortless comfort, productivity, and adventure, this two-story condo delivers an elevated Big Bear experience for families, couples, and remote workers alike.&lt;br /&gt;
Step inside to a warm, inviting interior where natural light pours through large stained-glass windows, highlighting thoughtfully curated d&amp;eacute;cor and cozy furnishings. The expansive living area is perfect for relaxing after a day on the lake or slopes, featuring plush seating, a fireplace for memorable mountain evenings, and a convenient mini fridge for beverages and snacks.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The modern kitchen is a true standout, equipped with sleek appliances, generous counter space, and everything needed to fuel your mountain days. From quick breakfasts before skiing to relaxed dinners with friends and family, this kitchen is designed for both function and enjoyment.&lt;br /&gt;
Restmoore offers three spacious bedrooms, each styled for deep rest with luxurious bedding and tasteful accents. The two full bathrooms feature contemporary fixtures, providing comfort and convenience for every guest. With remote workers in mind, the home includes a dedicated remote office setup in the primary bedroom, complete with a desk, wired keyboard, and mouse&amp;mdash;ideal for focused work with a mountain backdrop.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step out onto your private balcony to breathe in the crisp alpine air and enjoy the peaceful Boulder Bay surroundings. Community amenities elevate the experience year-round, including a seasonal pool, all-season spa, tennis courts, and pickleball courts. In winter, enjoy the unbeatable convenience of being able to walk to the ski shuttle, providing easy access to both major Big Bear ski resorts. Entertainment is built in for guests of all ages, with classic arcade games like Pac-Man, additional retro favorites, and a selection of kids&amp;rsquo; games, puzzles, books, and activities. Perfectly located near the lake, trails, and winter sports, Restmoore blends easy living, modern comfort, and a highly desirable Boulder Bay location. Whether you are here to ski, work remotely, relax by the pool, or enjoy Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s natural beauty, this is your home base for it all.&lt;br /&gt;
