&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to your dream mountain retreat! Step out of the front door to Snow Summit Ski Resort! Nestled right at the base of the Resort this lovely two-story reverse floor plan ski condo offers the perfect blend of luxury and convenience for an unparalleled alpine experience. Cozy mountain essentials, vaulted ceilings, and a cozy/social circular fireplace are available to add to your vacation experience here at Smith Summit Chalet!&lt;br /&gt;
