&lt;br /&gt;
A classic cabin in the woods, Moose Mountain Manor welcomes you to an unforgettable retreat in Big Bear. Located on a quiet yet central corner lot you are surrounded with soaring pine trees and incredible modern details like the stone fireplace, vaulted wood ceilings, and a spacious sun deck that makes you feel like you are in the trees. This home is a true indulgence into nature yet is only 1 mile from Bear Mountain Resort, minutes to Big Bear Village shops, and less than 5 minutes to local hiking, biking, and lake adventures.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
