Bruin Chalet Big Bear - Cozy Mountain Retreat&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Bruin Chalet! This cozy single level Bear City retreat is the perfect destination for a getaway to the mountains any time of the year- boasting all that you need to relax comfortably and unwind in a great alpine atmosphere. Charming mountain furnishings pair with knotty pine accents and decor to provide your group with a sense of cozy mountain vibes and relaxation as you enjoy your time under soaring pine trees and shooting stars. Located within a short ten-minute drive to local activities this cottage is a prime destination no matter the season you visit.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Ample parking and a cute circular driveway greet you upon arrival as you head up the adorable front yard and see your cute patio deck. Enter the cozy and warm open space of your cabin where you are greeted with vaulted knotty pine ceilings, big open windows, and a toasty brick fireplace where you will love warming your toes as you watch the snow falling outside. You&amp;#39;ll love the seating arrangements around the fire as you pop on a movie on the flat screen TV and enjoy your time together. The chef of your party will adore the equipped cabin kitchen and dining area offering the essentials for home cooked meals and slope side snacks including cookware and general appliances.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Being a single level chalet, you will love the easy and convenient access to both bedrooms and the hallway bathroom, all are made up for your group&amp;#39;s arrival with warm linens, blankets, and fresh bath towels for your stay. Big open windows throughout the property provide the perfect balance of natural lighting and forested views plus a stacked washer and dryer is on hand for those wet snow clothes or extended visits to Big Bear. Head outside where you can enjoy the front patio and sun deck or let the kids play freely in the open forested back yard- the possibilities are endless from here. Just ten minutes to local activities this cozy &amp;quot;Bruin Chalet&amp;quot; is the perfect blend of relaxation and peace with mountain charm and utmost convenience. Come experience this home away from home in the mountains for your next adventure today!&lt;br /&gt;
