property.description:
Inspiration Point Retreat - Boat Dock - Game Table&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Inspiration Point Retreat. Our spacious two-story lakefront chalet offers plenty of space and essentials to provide the perfect setting for family vacation or group getaway to the mountains. Boasting a private boat dock, endless views, and the necessities to create lifelong memories together under the stars this relaxing family retreat sits just minutes away from the ski resorts, grocery stores, and shopping area.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Snuggle up on the comfy couches as you warm your toes together in front of the toasty fireplace and take in the incredible lake views or pop on a movie on the mounted flat screen to enjoy a nice evening at the cabin. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining a group as you prepare your home cooked meals in the equipped chef&amp;#39;s kitchen, complete with cookware and appliances for your use. Almost every room of this chalet offers access to the great wrapped sun decks, you will love being right at one with nature here.&amp;nbsp;Two spacious bedrooms and two modern bathrooms are easily accessible upstairs in the main entry level however heading downstairs you&amp;#39;ll find a spacious second living room which makes the perfect game room area. Complete with another toasty fireplace and a ping pong table you will definitely spend some time entertaining the group here in this relaxing portion of the cabin. Two more bedrooms and another modern bathroom sits here on this lower downstairs level which also leads right out to the open forested hillside property.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Stepping outside you will find yourselves sitting right on what&amp;#39;s known as &amp;quot;Inspiration Point&amp;quot; where relaxation meets lake life within a quiet hillside neighborhood location. The private boat dock ensures you can enjoy your lake toys right from the cabin while a propane BBQ allows you to grill up your freshly caught dinner up on the deck. Located in the Boulder Bay area you are just ten minutes by car to the ski resorts, marina, and shopping areas making this the perfect destination no matter the season you choose to visit Big Bear!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
