Our Cabin in the Woods - Big Bear Relaxing Retreat w/ Hot Tub&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Our Cabin in the Woods- this is the perfect getaway chalet for a family or group of friends looking to experience the best of Big Bear any time of the year. Centrally located within a quick car ride to local activities and boasting all that you will need for relaxing and creating memories under the stars including a fun foosball table and your own private hot tub, your group will love your visit here at our cozy cabin in the woods.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Snuggle up on the plush sectional sofa as you warm your toes in front of the fireplace and pop on a movie on the flat screen TV or challenge each other at a game of foosball conveniently located under the staircase. Around the corner the equipped kitchen and dining room area offers everything you need to prepare home cooked meals and snacks for your adventures out on the lake including cookware and stainless-steel appliances. Enjoy easy access to the lower-level bedroom while both sleeping quarters are located upstairs along with an added bathroom and private balcony off of one of the rooms- perfect for reading a book or sipping your coffee in the mornings.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Outside this mountain oasis allows you to be at one with nature, boasting a great patio area and enclosed private hot tub just outside the kitchen patio slider, you will love soaking your muscles here and unwinding after a fun day out on the mountain. Located just below Bear Mountain Resort in what is known as the Moonridge area, you have quick and easy access to local coffee and donut shops, ski resort shuttles, golf, and the Big Bear Zoo just outside your cabin door. Hop in the car and you are within ten minutes to the grocery store, marina, and Village shops- this truly is an unbeatable cabin in the woods no matter the season you choose to visit!&lt;br /&gt;
