property.description:
The Nest on Towne Trail | Big Bear Village Retreat&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Nestled among towering pines &amp;quot;The Nest on Towne Trail&amp;quot; beckons with its quaint charm and serene ambiance. Tucked back from the road, this cozy one-bedroom cabin offers a perfect escape for romantics and nature lovers alike.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
As you approach &amp;quot;The Nest&amp;quot;, a rustic exterior of weathered timber and a warm embrace of natural beauty greets you. Inside, the cabin exudes a cozy elegance, with exposed wooden beams overhead and hardwood floors underfoot. Soft, ambient lighting casts a gentle glow over carefully curated furnishings that blend modern comfort with vintage cabin charm. The living area invites relaxation while the comfortable sofa positioned in front of a crackling fireplace, creates a cozy spot to unwind after a day of adventure on the nearby national forest trails. A well-appointed kitchen stands ready for preparing hearty meals, complete with essential amenities and dining area for those romantic dinners too. Whether hiking, mountain biking, kayaking on the lake, shopping in the Village or even staying at home and enjoying the hot tub, whatever your preference, guests will find the bedroom very comfortable for a restful night sleep essential before starting new adventures the next day.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Located just a short distance from the bustling Village, Big Bear Lake, Snow Summit and the popular forest Towne Trail, The Nest offers convenience without sacrificing quiet seclusion. Whether you&amp;#39;re seeking adventure on the nearby mountain trails or simply yearning for a peaceful retreat, this cabin provides the ideal blend of comfort, romance, and natural beauty&amp;mdash;a true haven for those seeking solace in the heart of Big Bear. Only a half mile stroll to local marinas for lake activities, Village shops for dining and entertainment, and world-famous Big Bear dining options like Tropicali and Grizzly Manor- this cottage truly offers a most incredible downtown location.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
