&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Green Squirrel Chateau, a fun, cozy, and spacious family-friendly mountain home in the heart of Big Bear Lake. Surrounded by tall pines where squirrels love to play&amp;mdash;earning the home its charming name&amp;mdash;this two-story cabin delivers comfort, convenience, and room to make memories year-round.&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for families, friends, and pets, this inviting retreat offers generous living space with warm mountain d&amp;eacute;cor, fireplaces, and flat-screen streaming TVs for relaxed nights in. The garage game room is a crowd favorite, featuring a pool table and console hookups for hours of entertainment for kids, teens, and adults alike.&lt;br /&gt;
