&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Woodland Retreat, a beautifully updated lakeside condo in the highly sought-after Boulder Bay area of Big Bear Lake, CA. Designed for easy comfort and unforgettable mountain stays, this modern retreat blend&amp;#39;s prime location, resort-style amenities, and a warm, inviting atmosphere&amp;mdash;perfect for families, couples, and groups. Surrounded by towering pines and just steps from the lake, this spacious condo offers an open-concept living area with cozy mountain furnishings, a toasty fireplace, and modern flat-screen TVs throughout. The fully equipped kitchen and dining space feature updated finishes, a breakfast bar, and everything needed for home-cooked meals, holiday gatherings, and relaxed entertaining.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy three comfortable bedrooms and two full bathrooms, offering plenty of room to unwind after a full day of Big Bear adventures. Step outside to your private patio with outdoor seating and peaceful complex views, ideal for morning coffee or crisp mountain evenings under the stars.&lt;br /&gt;
The location truly sets this home apart. Take a short walk to Pleasure Point Marina for easy lake access, boat rentals, and summer fun. In winter, enjoy the convenience of a walkable ski shuttle with access to both major Big Bear ski resorts. Community amenities include a seasonal pool, year-round spa, tennis courts, and pickleball courts, delivering a resort-style experience all year long. Minutes from Big Bear Village, hiking trails, skiing, dining, and shopping, Woodland Retreat places you at the center of it all while still offering a peaceful lakeside escape.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Woodland Retreat at Big Bear delivers comfort, location, and value&amp;mdash;your go-to mountain getaway in Boulder Bay, any season of the year.&amp;nbsp;As a special thank you, the homeowner proudly offers a special booking code for first responders.&lt;br /&gt;
