property.description:
Vivienda De Osos | Walk to the Lake | Spacious Fawnskin Retreat Chalet&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Vivienda De Osos, a charming and spacious 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom cabin nestled in the peaceful community of Fawnskin, just steps from the shores of Big Bear Lake. With accommodations for up to 10 guests, this warm and inviting retreat is perfect for families or groups seeking a quiet escape with easy access to both nature and local attractions. Set on a beautifully landscaped lot with whimsical dancing bear topiaries and a semi-enclosed yard, the home offers both privacy and character in a truly unique setting.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The fully furnished kitchen makes mealtimes a breeze, whether you&amp;#39;re cooking for a crowd or enjoying a relaxed breakfast before the day&amp;#39;s adventures. After a day outdoors, unwind in the jetted bathtub or challenge your group to a game in the converted garage game room, complete with a pool table. A circular driveway provides ample parking, and the outdoor BBQ area is perfect for grilling while taking in peaceful lake views. While pets are not permitted, the home is family-friendly and thoughtfully equipped for a comfortable and relaxing stay.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Just a short walk away, you&amp;#39;ll find Dana Point Park and the Fawnskin Dog Park, as well as access to the lake and local favorites like the Big Bear Tiki Tours. Whether you&amp;#39;re exploring the nearby trails, enjoying lake activities, or simply soaking in the calm of the mountains, Vivienda De Osos offers a serene and memorable mountain getaway for every season.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
