Bedroom 1: Queen Bed - Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: King Bed + Full Futon - Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Loft: Queen Sofa Sleeper - Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Living Room: Queen Sofa Sleeper - Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
