&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Moonridge Treehouse! Perfect for a group of friends, couple&amp;#39;s getaway, or even a family vacation, this relaxing hillside retreat boasts all that you need for a memorable vacation in the mountains any time of the year. Centrally located within a short ten-minute drive to local Big Bear activities including a short drive to Bear Mountain ski resort, golf, hiking, marinas, and even lake activities- this chalet offers a prime location no matter your activity choice.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
