&lt;br /&gt;
Golden Bear at Shay Meadows is an amazing and spacious home, newly constructed and freshly furnished from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind our owners have provided the perfect peaceful getaway for your next group or family vacation to Big Bear. Situated on the very East end of town your cabin will back up to a meadow where you might see wild donkeys among other wildlife in a spacious open wildland known locally as Shay Meadows. Sitting atop a large open and flat lot you will have access to ample year-round parking within a ten-minute drive to all local activities including the ski resorts and Village shops.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter into the main level of your chalet as you are greeted with luxurious interior furnishings, gorgeous hardwood floors, and high vaulted ceilings, you will immediately feel as if you have your own mountain lodge to yourselves. The entry foyer offers a great sitting area and work desk while the elegance continues on into the cozy living room area, leather couches and lounge chairs are sat perfectly in front of the toasty gas faux log fireplace and mounted Smart TV, another wonderful space provided for your group to snuggle up for a movie night or enjoy the snow falling through the big open windows. You will love the open floor plan as every room leads to the next, the formal dining room area offers a custom log table with seating for eight plus amazing views and deck access paired with the breakfast bar stools and multiple sitting areas larger group meals and entertaining is a breeze here! The chef of your group will love and appreciate the gourmet kitchen, boasting high quality appliances, a dishwasher, and gorgeous cabinets stocked full of cookware and utensils.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You will find one guest bedroom and a spacious primary suite available on this lower level for convenience, boasting high quality mattresses made up with warm linens, blankets, and fresh shower towels for your stay. Venture upstairs to find a spacious loft area, perfect for any age with added seating couches, a massive mounted Smart TV, and a foosball table- this will be the spot that everyone gathers to watch the game or unwind after a day of adventure out on the trails. Enjoy convenient access to a guest bedroom, bathroom, and the other primary suite on this upstairs level, the perfect amount of space for any group.&amp;nbsp;Outside you will find the ultimate spot for peace and relaxation, a private patio area offers a propane BBQ for your grilling pleasure. Golden Bear at Shay Meadows is an amazing vacation escape, packed with all that you need for a memorable and relaxing vacation and offering a great secluded location within ten minutes to local activities- come experience your new home away from home today!&lt;br /&gt;
