&lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy a slice of Big Bear Lake tranquility here at Round Rock Lodge!! Freshly renovated and furnished with your vacation stay in mind, this relaxing retreat offers all that you need under one cozy roof. Sitting within steps from local hiking trails, Boulder Bay Park with lake access, and a short drive to local attractions and activities, this retreat is the perfect destination for a relaxing vacation any time of the year.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
