property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Willow Bear Lodge Modern Boulder Bay Retreat &amp;bull; Hot Tub &amp;bull; Walk to Lake &amp;amp; Resort Shuttle&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Willow Bear Lodge, your elevated Big Bear escape where modern comfort meets iconic mountain charm. Set in one of Boulder Bay&amp;rsquo;s most desirable neighborhoods, this refreshed cabin puts adventure at your doorstep. Stroll just 5 minutes to Boulder Bay Park and lake access or hop on the resort shuttle only two doors down for seamless winter skiing and summer mountain biking. Every season becomes effortless from this unbeatable location.&lt;br /&gt;
Inside, the lodge delivers an inviting, polished atmosphere designed for connection and relaxation. A cozy stone fireplace, warm timber accents, upgraded wood style flooring, and intentional lighting come together to create a stylish, mountain modern feel. The open concept layout unites the living room, dining space, and kitchen, perfect for gathering after a day outdoors. Cook with ease in the fully equipped kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, and a movable island that adapts to your needs.&lt;br /&gt;
Upstairs, two bright and comfortable bedrooms await, each showcasing soaring wood beamed ceilings and a private balcony for your own personal slice of nature. The primary suite glows with natural light and sweeping treetop views, while the second bedroom overlooks the fully fenced backyard.&lt;br /&gt;
Outdoor living shines here, too. Start your mornings on the sunny deck, fire up the BBQ for delicious evenings in, relax in the private hot tub after a day of adventure, or enjoy the crisp alpine air from the upper balcony. The spacious yard provides a great space for outdoor enjoyment, perfect for play, relaxation, and unforgettable nights of stargazing beneath Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s sparkling sky.&lt;br /&gt;
Centrally located near local dining, boutique shopping, scenic hikes, and both major ski resorts, Willow Bear Lodge is your all-season home base for exploration and fun. Whether planning a family adventure, a lakeside getaway, or a snow filled retreat, this modern cabin delivers comfort, convenience, and standout Big Bear magic from the moment you arrive.&lt;br /&gt;
