Inside, sun-filled rooms and tall windows create an airy, welcoming atmosphere throughout. The game room features arcade games, board games, and a comfortable hangout space, while basketball pop-a-shot, cornhole, and darts are located in the garage for extra fun. Flat-screen TVs are available in the great room, game room, and master bedroom, offering casual entertainment without overwhelming the home&amp;rsquo;s natural charm. The large, fully stocked kitchen makes cooking for groups easy and enjoyable after days spent exploring the mountains or relaxing by the lake.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
