&lt;br /&gt;
Step into this stunning single-story contemporary mountain retreat, perfectly located just minutes from the lake, village, parks, and all of Big Bear&amp;rsquo;s top attractions. Recently renovated with care and style, this beautiful home offers three spacious bedrooms, two elegant bathrooms, and a bright, open Great Room centered around a striking rock wood-burning fireplace&amp;mdash;an inviting spot to gather with family and friends.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Nestled within walking distance of the village, Alpine Slide, local restaurants, markets, and hiking trails, this home combines convenience with peaceful mountain charm. The lake and ski slopes are only a short drive away, making it the perfect year-round getaway. Set on a quiet, tree-lined street near the Mill Creek area, the property offers a sense of tranquility and privacy. As you arrive, a separate two-car garage provides flexibility and could easily be transformed into a game room or bonus space. A charming pathway leads to the front door, where towering Ponderosa pines provide shade for the front entertainment area. Inside, a cozy stone fireplace adds warmth and ambiance during chilly winter evenings, while the open-concept floor plan allows for easy entertaining in every season.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Nearly every detail of this home has been beautifully upgraded, including the roof, kitchen, bathrooms, flooring, windows, fixtures, and lighting. The kitchen features stylish new cabinets and countertops, while 100% waterproof vinyl flooring extends throughout the home for durability and comfort. Each of the three bedrooms is thoughtfully appointed, and the two full bathrooms are designed with modern tile and fixtures. The large, fenced backyard is perfect for kids and pets to play, offering both privacy and plenty of outdoor space. Enjoy relaxing outdoors in the covered dining area surrounded by tall, majestic trees, or take advantage of the spacious laundry and mudroom&amp;mdash;ideal for keeping things tidy after a day of mountain adventures. From the moment you walk in, you&amp;rsquo;ll feel the warmth and charm of this exceptional Big Bear retreat. Book your stay today and experience the magic of mountain living in this beautiful cabin getaway.&lt;br /&gt;
