property.description:
Kelley&amp;#39;s Kabin- Hot Tub- Walk to Lake/Village&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Ready for a truly nostalgic trip to the mountains with the crew to enjoy the best of Big Bear? Bring the kids up to experience a forest vacation here at Kelley&amp;#39;s&amp;nbsp;Kabin- our furnished and cozy central cottage sits among the pines on a private treed lot within a short walk to Big Bear Lake and the downtown Village shops. Kitchen and dining essentials pair with cozy mountain furnishings to provide a great space to enjoy your time together under the stars sits on the sun deck out front, you will love this adorable cabin.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter the cozy living room area to be greeted with knotty pine ceilings and wall accents that immediate give you a sense of mountain vibes within an open floor plan. Snuggle up on the comfortable couch as you warm your toes in front of the toasty faux log gas fireplace (shared with the master bedroom) and pop on a movie on the ROKU Streaming TV. Enjoy the cute dining table and equipped kitchen for your meals together with cookware and appliances provided or head around the corner for easy access to a guest full bath.&amp;nbsp; The spacious primary bedroom has it own 1/2 bath with a Streaming TV, and shared with the living room gas fireplace.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Upstairs you will find two additional sleeping areas ready for you to enjoy a great night of rest, one is perfect for the kids with two set of bunkbeds. The other bedroom has a queen bed.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
From the living room you can step&amp;nbsp;outside where you can enjoy a spacious front yard and front deck area, where you can grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake on the Propane BBQ. Enjoy soaking in the adorable hot tub under the stars on the front deck, you will love unwinding after a fun day on the mountain out here in the spa. Kelley&amp;#39;s Kabin is a great destination for any group no matter the season with a prime location and essentials you will love your visit here at your next home away from home.&lt;br /&gt;
