property.description:
Rosie&amp;#39;s Hideaway ~ Spacious Retreat Near the Mountain &amp;amp; Lake with Grill &amp;amp; Full Kitchen&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Inviting and rustic in all the best ways, this Big Bear retreat will be just the place to bring the whole family for an unforgettable vacation. From the charming brick accents and fireplace of the living room to the open layout of the full kitchen, this home away will have everyone slipping into relaxation mode in no time.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step out to the back deck and you will have a perfect space to reminisce over a cold beverage as hot dogs and hamburgers cook on the private gas grill in the summer air. After a full day of shredding on the slopes nearby, everyone will love gathering in the living room to tell stories about the day&amp;#39;s events as the fire crackles and a movie plays on the flatscreen TV.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
It&amp;#39;s all about location at this getaway, as you will be within minutes of the best attractions in Big Bear Lake. Though you will have everything you need to have the time of your life at your fingertips, venture out and spend a day on the lake sitting just over a mile away. Whether you choose to boat, swim, paddleboard, or simply lounge on the sandy shore, the day will be well-spent in the sunshine.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Come winter, the slopes will be calling your name. Luckily, Snow Summit Ski Resort is a quick half-mile drive away, making for easy access to fresh powder. Not to mention the wide array of shops and restaurants in Big Bear Lake proper will be just the ticket for a night out or day of window shopping.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
