property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;The Wilkie Cabin ~ Calming home hideaway in the woods with fireplace, balcony, grill, &amp;amp; board games&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Originally built in the 1960s by the owners&amp;#39; father and uncle, this three-story treasured family cabin boasts classic rustic vibes while being lovingly restored with an updated kitchen, bathrooms, laundry, and huge rear deck that celebrates the views of Gold Mountain!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You&amp;#39;ll feel right at home at this cozy perch in the mountains with its nostalgic wood burning fireplace, vintage furniture and charming artworks depicting tranquil forest scenes and cherished wildlife. Head up to the loft area, and you will immediately fall in love with the Modernist A-frame design featuring a fun &amp;#39;British pub&amp;#39; plaid carpet, rocking chairs, bunk beds for the kids, and tall windows that face century-old pines. A full, recently remodeled kitchen is ready for whipping up tasty meals with ease and the free Wi-Fi and flatscreen TV will provide more than enough entertainment as the stars come out.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
What&amp;#39;s nearby:&lt;br /&gt;
Located mere steps from the entrance of Pebble Plains Nature Preserve, everyone can enjoy acres of untouched forest with easy trails, vista points, 17 unique eco-systems, and a variety of forest flora and fauna in no time! For a bit of winter fun, head over to Big Bear Snow Play for some sledding that the whole family can enjoy or venture a bit further to Big Bear Mountain Resort (four miles) or Bear Mountain Ski Resort (five miles) to ski to your heart&amp;#39;s content. Warmer times of the year will uncover the pristine hiking trails in the areas and Big Bear Lake is a blast for boating, fishing, swimming, and more!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Full Bed- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: Queen Bed- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3: Queen Bed- Upstairs 3rd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Loft: Two Twin/Twin Bunks + Twin Bed, Game Table, Sitting Area- Upstairs 3rd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Half Bath- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath- Middle Level Off Living Room&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
~Sleeps 10&lt;br /&gt;
~3 Car Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
~NO PETS ALLOWED&lt;br /&gt;
~1,380 Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
~County Permit #: CESTRP-2021-00590&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;

