&lt;br /&gt;
Find this luxury log home in the scenic Moonridge area, minutes from the slopes of Bear Mountain Ski Resort. Hop onto a forest trail just down the road. You&amp;#39;re also located one mile from Bear Mountain Ski Resort, Bear Mountain Golf Course, and the brand-new Big Bear Alpine Zoo.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The 2,624-square-foot layout has a floor-to-ceiling river rock fireplace, a well-appointed loft, and a standalone game room. This welcoming space also has NBA Jam and Marvel Super Heroes arcade cabinets, along with an air hockey table. Vaulted ceilings soar in the great room, detailed with a sofa, a smart TV, and a floor-to-ceiling river rock fireplace. There&amp;#39;s even a quiet spot to play a game of chess. Warm wood cabinetry complements granite countertops and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. A gas range and side-by-side fridge make meal prep simple.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This magnificent mountain home is perched on a half-acre parcel surrounded by trees and fencing. Find a seasonal stream winding through the grounds. Two wraparound porches provide ample room to enjoy the alfresco air. Fire up the gas grill, then share an outdoor meal at a dining table seating four.&lt;br /&gt;
