property.description:
Nine Pines Lodge Big Bear Relaxing Log Cabin&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Nine Pines Lodge!!! Nestled in the trees near Bear Mountain Resort and the Moonridge area your group will love this cozy and comfortable two-story log cabin retreat, surrounded by nine large pine trees yet still within a few minutes&amp;#39; drive to all local Big Bear activities. Boasting the comforts from home along with cozy mountain furnishings and modern Streaming TVs your group will love your stay here no matter the season you choose to visit!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
After climbing the beautiful wood staircase, you will enter your chalet in the super comfortable living room area where you are immediately greeted with log d&amp;eacute;cor and mountain vibes from the second you walk in. This room is beautifully dominated by the floor to ceiling faux log gas fireplace (this is the only heat source for this home) with a gorgeous log mantel piece that hosts a mounted flat screen Streaming TV. Your group will love snuggling up here on the couches and warming your toes in front of the fire as you pop on a movie with complimentary hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment by the owners. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.) The open floor plan flows seamlessly around the corner to the dining room and equipped kitchen areas where the group can enjoy sitting together and feasting on your home cooked meals at the log dining table. The chef of your group will love this adorable kitchen which is stocked with cookware and utensils plus basic appliances for your use during your visit and even a dishwasher to ensure a breezy cleanup. From here you can access the back deck with a Charcoal BBQ and treed mountain views available so you can grill up dinner and unwind in the evenings.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Your spacious chalet home offers the perfect layout for your party with a full bathroom on each level of the property as well as two bedrooms on each level of the property, each room is made up for your group with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your visit when you arrive. The upstairs bathroom offers a jetted spa tub for you to soak away your fun day out on the mountain plus a stacked washer and dryer is on hand for those wet snow clothes or extended visits to the mountains. Nine Pines Lodge offers extreme relaxation and serenity surrounded by trees, boasting the best in amenities and d&amp;eacute;cor, plus is equipped with essentials and then some, all while being located in a wonderful &amp;quot;close to it all&amp;quot; neighborhood, this mountain vacation home is the best destination choice for your next retreat to Big Bear!!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
