property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Meadow-Front Metcalf Bay Cabin | Hot Tub, Air Hockey, Firepit &amp;amp; Lake Views&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Nestled on a peaceful meadow, this stylish 2BR cabin is within a quick stroll of Metcalf Bay. This completely gated property features air hockey, foosball, three smart TVs, and a fireplace. When you want to hit the slopes, Snow Summit is a mere 10-minute drive. Spend leisurely summer afternoons on the patio, equipped with a private hot tub, a firepit, a grill, and alfresco dining. Catch a beautiful view of the lake from the backyard!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Unwind in the welcoming living area, which provides comfy seating for the group, a wood-burning fireplace, a smart TV, and a dual coffee/foosball table. A detached game room is fitted with an air hockey table. The well-equipped kitchen has everything needed to prepare favorite dishes, including ample cookware and helpful gadgets. When meals are ready, the table seats four.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sip morning coffee on the front patio. Make use of the gas grill and host an afternoon cookout. When it&amp;#39;s time to eat, a table seats four for alfresco meals. In the evening, take relaxing soaks in the brand-new hot tub or kick back around the gas firepit. Admire the beautiful lake views anytime.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This home is just 10 minutes from the slopes at Snow Summit and 13 minutes from Bear Mountain. Pleasure Point Marina is a 4-minute drive. For dining and shopping, the heart of town is only 3 minutes from home. For additional entertainment, take a ride on the Alpine Slide at Magic Mountain or explore a variety of hiking trails in the area.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
