property.description:
Lazy Bear Cabin ~ Dog-friendly home with private hot tub, ping-pong, basketball &amp;amp; firepit&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
From custom bathrooms that ensure the perfect shower to a brand-new hot tub, this cozy 2BR/2BA home invites you to hang up your coat and stay awhile. Named Lazy Bear Cabin, this home is ideally suited for a family with two kids and a dog. Beautifully remodeled, this retreat offers ample space to relax with a large back deck, two grills, a fire pit, and a front porch that can be completely gated off. You&amp;#39;ll find the village, lake, marina, and slopes all close at hand.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Lined with brickwork, the living area offers comfy seating with a sleeper sofa and armchair. Watch shows on the 55in TV while the gas fireplace warms the space. The updated kitchen boasts a full suite of stainless-steel appliances, including a Viking microwave and gas range/oven. In the dining area, you&amp;#39;ll find a 44in TV and a table that seats up to six.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The primary suite has a California king bed, office nook, 44in TV, walk-in closet, and direct access to the deck. The en-suite bathroom boasts a walk-in shower. The second bedroom offers two twin beds, a 44in TV, and direct access to the deck. The guest bathroom also has a walk-in shower. Both walk-in showers have three showerheads and a diverter valve that ensures a constant/pleasant temperature. You&amp;#39;ll also find grab bars and safety handrails in both bathrooms.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Take your pick between a gas and charcoal grill and throw a cookout on the large new deck. While dinner sizzles, relax in two chairs shaded by a large umbrella. Share meals at the four-person table. As evening falls, soak in the private hot tub or gather around the fire pit. Solar lights illuminate the deck, patio, and hot tub. Additional outdoor space includes a front porch with seating for five and a gate that can be completely closed off. A basketball hoop hangs above the driveway. In the garage you&amp;#39;ll find a provided basketball as well as a ping-pong table and a card table for two.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Cal King Bed, Office Nook, Streaming TV, Deck Access, Private Bath&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: Two Twin Beds, Streaming TV, Deck Access&lt;br /&gt;
Living Room: Queen Sleeper Sofa&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Private 3/4 Bath w/ Walk-In Shower- Bedroom 1&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway 3/4 Bath (Shower Only)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
~Sleeps 4&lt;br /&gt;
~2 Car Driveway Parking&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
~1 Pet Welcome w/ Additional Fees&lt;br /&gt;
~1,120 Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
~City Permit #:&amp;nbsp;VRR-2024-1597&lt;br /&gt;
