Dusk to Dawn Central Moonridge Retreat w/ Hot Tub&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Dusk To Dawn is a cozy ultra-central mountain cabin that is perfect for a couple or small family to getaway to Big Bear! Located within a quiet but central Moonridge neighborhood, your group will be within minutes of Bear Mountain Resort for golf, hiking, skiing or the local Alpine Zoo. Boasting the necessities from home along with cozy and comfortable mountain touches along with a great private yard including your own private hot tub your group will love your visit here!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter into a cute and cozy living room area where you are greeted with knotty pine cathedral ceilings, big open windows, and comfy furnishings to make you feel right at home. You will love snuggling up on the cozy couches where you can warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace as you watch the snow falling outside or pop on a movie on the flat screen Streaming TV with complimentary hi speed WIFI provided for your enjoyment. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming services.) Around the corner the adorable kitchen and dining area has all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals or holiday feasts including cookware, utensils, general appliances, and a cute dining table for your meals together.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy quick and easy access here to the spacious fenced private backyard where you can enjoy grilling up dinner on the charcoal BBQ or soaking up your day in the brand new hot tub under the pines. The sun deck is a great space to sip your first cup of coffee in the mornings among the birds or unwind in the evening as you take in this serene environment. Both sleeping quarters and the hallway bathroom are made up for your groups arrival with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your visit when you arrive, keeping things super convenient. Take a quick stroll down to the new Moonridge Corridor with local bakery and coffee shops as well as the Alpine Zoo within a short distance. You are also within a ten minute car ride to the lake, marinas, and resorts making this chalet the ultimate choice for your vacation stay no matter the season you choose to visit!&lt;br /&gt;
