property.description:
Cozy Cabin &amp;ndash; End of Cul-De-Sac Retreat with Hot Tub, Fenced Yard, and Boat Parking | Near Big Bear Lake Village &amp;amp; Snow Summit&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Escape to serenity at&amp;nbsp;Quiet Cabin, a beautifully remodeled 3BR/2BA vacation home nestled among tall pines at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac. Perfectly located just 1.5 miles from Big Bear Lake Village, Snow Summit, and Meadow Park, this private getaway offers the ideal blend of seclusion and convenience.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step inside to discover a warm, rustic-chic interior featuring knotty pine details, a wood-burning fireplace, and modern upgrades throughout. The inviting living area includes a large sectional, armchair, and 64-inch smart TV for cozy movie nights. Cook with ease in the fully stocked kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, then gather for meals around the six-person dining table.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping arrangements comfortably accommodate up to six guests across three well-appointed bedrooms, including a primary suite with a queen bed and smart TV. Children and families will love the fun upstairs bunk room with a twin-over-twin bed, trundle, arcade machine, and Roku TV.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Outside, relax in the private hot tub after a day on the slopes, fire up outdoor games like bean bag toss or horseshoes in the spacious fenced yard, and enjoy alfresco dining under the stars. With a large driveway offering ample parking even for a boat this property is ready for your next mountain adventure. Book your stay today and experience the tranquil charm, comfort, and convenience of Quiet Cabin your perfect Big Bear retreat awaits!

