property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Moonridge Alameda ~ Moonridge home - private hot tub - dog-friendly - 6 minutes to Bear Mountain&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Luxuriate in your private hot tub after a day of skiing or hiking at this 4BR/2BA home! The convenient location in the Moonridge neighborhood is just a 6-minute drive from Bear Mountain, Alpine Zoo, and national forest trails. The spacious back deck offers big views, and the backyard horseshoe pit promises hours of amusement. Inside, cathedral-style ceilings create an inviting lodge-like ambience. Other home highlights include updated furnishings, and a cozy fireplace.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
LIVING AREA&lt;br /&gt;
Anchored by a wood-burning fireplace with river rock surround, the living area is the social heart of the home. Relax on the sectional and stream new shows on the flat-screen smart TV.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
KITCHEN &amp;amp; DINING&lt;br /&gt;
Prepare trail snacks and hearty meals in the kitchen, appointed with an array of stainless-steel appliances. The kitchen bar seats four to morning coffee. When you&amp;#39;re ready to eat, gather around the table for eight in the dining area.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
OUTDOOR AREA &amp;amp; AMENITIES&lt;br /&gt;
As you soak in the hot tub on the deck, admire a beautiful panoramic view of the surrounding beauty. Barbecue tasty meals on the gas grill and dine alfresco at the table for four. The horseshoe pit and the cornhole set in the backyard encourage friendly group tournaments.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
THE LOCATION&lt;br /&gt;
Located 2 miles from Bear Mountain, it&amp;#39;s just a 6-minute drive from your rental to the slopes. In the area, you&amp;#39;ll also find the Alpine Zoo and rewarding hikes in the Truck Trails area. Find even more ski terrain at Snow Summit, just 3 miles away. Travel 5 miles to Big Bear Village to find a plethora of local shops and restaurants. Lake fun awaits at Ski Beach Park, also 5 miles away.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Full Bed- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
