property.description:
Arktos Jewel Resort Chalet w/ Hot Tub ~ Pool Table&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Nestled conveniently within minutes of local ski resorts, hiking trails, and the lake, our cozy log cabin chalet is the perfect retreat for any group, regardless of the season. Immerse yourself in the warmth of knotty pine charm and mountain vibes throughout the cabin, where every detail has been considered to enhance your vacation stay.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The lower level welcomes you with abundant natural light streaming through floor-to-ceiling windows, complemented by knotty pine cathedral ceilings. The inviting open floor plan creates a sense of home, with oversized plush couches inviting you to snuggle up and enjoy a movie night by the toasty wood-burning fireplace while the snow falls outside. A beautiful log dining table and breakfast bar provide ample seating, offering stunning valley views through French doors that lead to the expansive redwood deck. For the chef in your group, the well-equipped kitchen ensures culinary delights with cookware, appliances, and even a dishwasher, all seamlessly integrated into the fabulous open floor plan. Convenience is key, with easy access to the laundry room, guest bath, and two inviting sleeping quarters, each with access to the redwood deck and backyard where your private spa awaits.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Upstairs, the spacious primary suite beckons with soaring windows, ceilings, a private full bath, and a balcony boasting breathtaking mountain views. Every room is thoughtfully prepared for your arrival, adorned with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels. The open game room loft offers additional entertainment with a full-size pool table, ensuring endless fun for your group. Step outside to discover a serene hillside property surrounded by trees and alpine nature on a spacious open lot. Outdoor patio furnishings invite you to relax and soak in the surroundings, while a Charcoal BBQ stands ready for evening grilling. The back deck is your private haven, hosting a hot tub where you can unwind under a million stars, reflecting on your day of lake or mountain adventures. Arktos Jewel lives up to its name, providing guests with everything needed for an unforgettable mountain vacation at Big Bear. Experience the magic of this fabulous cabin today!&lt;br /&gt;
