property.description:
Entertainment Cabin ~ Lovely home with hot tub, game room, balcony, &amp;amp; firepit - dog friendly&lt;br /&gt;
Conveniently situated on a large corner lot, this three-bedroom, two-bath home presents an entertainer&amp;#39;s oasis perfect for year-round vacation bliss. The spacious and fenced outdoor area provides a private hot tub, firepit, fenced dog kennel, a cornhole game, and multiple alfresco living and dining options. Concoct a refreshing beverage at the wet bar in the fully equipped game room, appointed with a foosball table and a pool table that also converts into a Ping-Pong table. An added perk includes a two-car garage.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
After fun-filled days, kick back in the welcoming living area, which offers a wood-burning fireplace and a smart TV. Hours of fun are spent in the fully stocked game room, detailed with a pool/Ping-Pong table, foosball table, smart TV, and a wet bar. Have fun playing classic games like Pac-Man, Space Invaders, and Dragon&amp;#39;s Lair on the cocktail-style arcade cabinet! A queen sofa bed offers an additional sleeping option.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The well-equipped kitchen is appointed with a full suite of stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample cookware. When your delectable dishes are ready, dine together at the table. The kitchen island also accommodates guests.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This home sleeps six adults and two children. The primary bedroom is fitted with a king bed, a full-size sofa bed, and a smart TV. The en-suite bathroom is configured with a walk-in shower. The second bedroom is furnished with a king bed and a smart TV, while the third bedroom has a twin-over-twin bunk bed. An adjacent bathroom has a walk-in shower. Additionally, there is a queen sofa bed in the living area.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
A true outdoor paradise, the fenced yard offers plenty of room to both relax and entertain. Host an afternoon cookout and dine alfresco on the deck. In the evening, pamper yourself with soaks in the private hot tub or gather around the gas firepit. Bonus features include a fenced kennel and a cornhole game. Less than 15 minutes from both Bear Mountain and Snow Summit, this home offers amazing access to skiing, snowboarding, hiking, and mountain biking. Find restaurants, shops, and popular attractions mere minutes away, while Big Bear Lake is a breezy 13-minute drive.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: King Bed + Sofa Sleeper, Streaming TV, Private 3/4 Bath&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: King Bed, Streaming TV&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3: Twin/Twin Bunk&lt;br /&gt;
Living Room: Queen Sofa Sleeper, Streaming TV, Fireplace&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Private 3/4 Bath- Bedroom 1- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
~Sleeps 8&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
~3 Car Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
~4 Pets Welcome w/ Additional Fees&lt;br /&gt;
~2,320 Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
~County Permit #:&amp;nbsp;CESTRP-2023-01868&lt;br /&gt;
