property.description:
Oriole Cottage Big Bear&amp;nbsp;| Cozy Cabin&amp;nbsp;| Walk to Lake&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for a group of friends or a small family to enjoy the best that Big Bear has to offer you will love your visit here at our Oriole Cottage- centrally located less than a mile from the lake or Village and furnished with comfortable mountain essentials to ensure a memorable and relaxing vacation is in store. Hop in the car and you are under ten minutes to the grocery stores, ski resorts, local zoo, and all local hiking trails offered in the valley.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter your home where you are greeted with a warm and cozy living room that is ordained in big open windows, vaulted cathedral beamed ceilings, and a great open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining a group for a dinner party or holiday meal. Snuggle up on the comfy couches as you warm your toes in front of the toasty wood burning fireplace as you watch the snow falling outside and pop on a movie on the flat screen TV with complimentary Cable and hi speed WIFI internet provided for your enjoyment by the owners. Enjoy forested views as you dine together at the adorable log dining table to the side of the room or sit at the breakfast bar and connect with the chef of your group as they prepare your home cooked meals with the perfect open floor space for everyone. The practical kitchen has all that you need for your preparations including ample counter space, oak cabinets stocked with cookware and utensils, general appliances, and even a dishwasher to ensure your cleanup is a breeze.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This single level chalet offers easy and convenient access to both bedrooms and your adorable hallway full bathroom, each is made up for your group with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh shower towels for your visit when you arrive. Enjoy playing on the foosball game or watching a movie separately in the second guest room plus a washer and dryer is right on hand for those wet snow clothes in the winter or extended visits to the mountains year round. Venture to the great outdoors where you will love the tree lined and fully fenced private backyard area with a fabulous patio that includes outdoor picnic tables and a Charcoal BBQ where you can relax and unwind in the evenings as you grill up your freshly caught dinner from the lake under the pines. Oriole Cottage has everything you need for a relaxing and memorable trip to the mountains no matter the season you choose to visit- make this your next home away from home today!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Queen Bed&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 2: Full Bed + Full Bed, TV w/ Cable, Foosball Table&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
-Sleeps 4&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
-2 Cars Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
-No Pets Allowed&lt;br /&gt;
-864 Total Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
