&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
Bear Mountain Chalet | Walk to Ski &amp;amp; Golf&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Perfect for a group of friends or family looking to enjoy a comfortable mountain experience our Bear Mountain Chalet is a spacious three-story family cabin that provides a prime location anytime of the year, along with the essentials and entertainment, this home has what you need for the perfect vacation! Take a short walk over to the Golf Course, Ski Lifts, or local hiking trails right outside your door or hop in the car and you are at the lake or downtown Village shops in under ten minutes!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Enter this tri level chalet on the lower entry level where you can unload your snow gear and lake toys and start to relax or enjoy the on site entertainment which includes a foosball table, arcade skeeball game, and a private indoor patio, this is the spot where most of your group will want to spend their time together. Venture up to the middle level to find two bedrooms, a guest bathroom. The third level hosts your cozy living and dining room areas and the equipped chef&amp;#39;s kitchen; this chalet is sprawling in the perfect amount of space for a large group to enjoy the mountains together. The upstairs loft bedroom and the guest bathroom are easily accessible from here, all your rooms are made up for your visit with warm linens, blankets, pillows, and fresh bath towels when you arrive. Comfy sitting couches sit perfectly in front of the toasty gas faux log fireplace in the living room area, with massive floor to ceiling windows and a great blend of natural lighting you will love snuggling up here in front of the fire and watching the snow falling outside. A massive mounted Streaming TV sits above the fireplace so you can enjoy a movie night in with the family, complimentary hi speed WIFI internet is provided for your convenience. (Guests must have their own accounts to enjoy Streaming Services.)&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The adorable dining table and breakfast bar ensures that you have ample sitting spaces to enjoy big meals together as a group while double sliding glass doors here give you immediate access to the wonderful sun deck where you can soak up the rays and catch peek a boo views of the ski slopes. Your group will love the equipped kitchen here at Bear Mountain Chalet, boasting all that you need to whip up your home cooked meals right here at the cabin. Oak cabinets are stocked full with cookware and utensils for you while ample counter spaces and general appliances including a dishwasher for convenience is available. You will love entertaining a dinner party or whipping up your meals while visiting with the group here as the open floor plan allows the perfect amount of flow between rooms. Direct patio access is available here which leads out to the tree lined slope side back yard area, complete with outdoor patio furnishings and a great space to relax and unwind. Bear Mountain Chalet is a great year round escape no matter the season you choose to visit Big Bear- come experience this cozy and relaxing chalet today.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
