property.description:
&lt;strong&gt;Switzerland Ski Chalet at Snow Summit | Freshly Remodeled Basecamp Retreat w/ Foosball&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to Switzerland Ski Chalet. Freshly renovated from head to toe with your vacation stay in mind, our cozy and comfortable chalet offers great natural lighting through big open windows, modern upgrades, and cozy mountain essentials to provide the perfect setting for a relaxing vacation to Big Bear any time of the year! Sitting just across the street from the ski lifts and summertime bike park this retreat offers the utmost convenient location- no hassle with long lines, shuttles, or paying for parking as you can walk right over to the lifts from your cabin door!&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Boasting two levels of sprawling space this chalet has everything you need for an amazing vacation together including an equipped kitchen, dining room, and living room area where you can warm your toes in front of the fireplace as you snuggle up on the oversized plush couch and pop on a movie to relax or enjoy the foosball table for more fun. Upstairs you have a great guest bunkroom, open loft sleeping room overlooking the living area, and thru the loft is the massive private suite which makes up the third bedroom. This upstairs suite is essentially another cabin in itself with a big, oversized bed, cozy living space, added fireplace, plus another kitchenette and wet bar for entertaining.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Venture to the great outdoors where you can enjoy the upper-level sun deck or lower-level patio area off of the living room which offers ski slope views, outdoor patio furnishings, and a relaxing forested yard perfect for relaxing and sipping your first cup of coffee in the morning. Walk across the street for resort activities including ski and bike park lifts, dining, tubing, and more. Hop in the car and you are less than 10-minutes to the grocery stores, marina, or even the downtown Village shops- this cabin truly offers an unbeatable central location. Come experience your new home away from home at Big Bear today here at Switzerland Ski Chalet!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Sleeping Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 1: Queen Bed + Twin/Twin Bunk- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Open Loft- Full Bed- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
Bedroom 3: King Bed, Private Full Bath, Kitchenette- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Bathroom Arrangements:&lt;br /&gt;
Hallway Full Bath- Downstairs Entry Level&lt;br /&gt;
Private Full Bath- Bedroom 3- Upstairs 2nd Level&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
-Sleeps 8&lt;br /&gt;
-2 Cars Driveway Parking&lt;br /&gt;
-NO PETS ALLOWED- Fines Imposed for Pets Found on Premises&lt;br /&gt;
-1,532 Square Feet&lt;br /&gt;
City Permit #:&amp;nbsp;VRR-2025-0198&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;

